458/* MAD_t
459* Structure to hold information from the common MAD header.
460* This is necessary because the MAD header contains information which significantly changes the dissection algorithm. */
461#define STL_MAX_MAD_PAYLOAD2048 2048
462typedef struct _MAD {
463 guint8 BaseVersion;
464 guint8 MgmtClass;
465 guint8 ClassVersion;
466 guint8 Method;
467 guint16 Status; /* D = bit 15 when DR */
468 guint8 HopPointer; /* Reserved in DR MADs */
469 guint8 HopCount; /* Reserved in DR MADs */
470 guint64 TransactionID;
471 guint16 AttributeID;
472 guint16 Reserved2;
473 guint32 AttributeModifier;
474} MAD_t;
475#define STL_MAX_RMPP_PAYLOAD2036 2036
476#define RMPP_FLAG_LAST_MASK0x04 0x04
477#define RMPP_FLAG_LAST_SHIFT2 2
478#define RMPP_FLAG_FIRST_MASK0x02 0x02
479#define RMPP_FLAG_FIRST_SHIFT1 1
480#define RMPP_FLAG_ACTIVE_MASK0x01 0x01
481#define RMPP_FLAG_ACTIVE_SHIFT0 0
482typedef struct _RMPP {
483 guint8 Version;
484 guint8 Type;
485 guint8 resptime_flags;
486 guint8 Status;
487 guint32 SegmentNumber;
488 guint32 PayloadLength;
489} RMPP_t;
490
491#define STL_MAX_SA_PA_PAYLOAD1992 1992
492typedef struct _SA_HEADER {
493 guint64 SM_Key;
494 guint16 AttributeOffset;
495 guint16 Reserved;
496 guint64 ComponentMask;
497} SA_HEADER_t, PA_HEADER_t;

2510static void cf_opa_mad_swinfo_ar_frequency(gchar *buf, guint16 value)
2511{
2512 g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "%u ms", 2 ^ (value)*64);

2514static void cf_opa_mad_linkspeed(gchar *buf, guint16 value)
2515{
2516 int len = 0;
2517 if (value & 0x1) /* 12.5 Gbps */
2518 len = g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "12.5");
2519 if (value & 0x2) /* 25.78125 Gbps */
2520 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%s25.78125", (len ? ", " : ""));
2521 if (len)
2522 g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, " Gbps");
2523 else
2524 g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "No State Change");
2525}
2526static void cf_opa_mad_linkwidth(gchar *buf, guint16 value)
2527{
2528 int len = 0;
2529 if (value & 0x1) /* 1x */
2530 len = g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "1X");
2531 if (value & 0x2) /* 2x */
2532 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%s2X", (len ? ", " : ""));
2533 if (value & 0x4) /* 3x */
2534 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%s3X", (len ? ", " : ""));
2535 if (value & 0x8) /* 4x */
2536 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%s4X", (len ? ", " : ""));
2537 if (!len)
2538 g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "No State Change");
2539}
2540static void cf_opa_mad_portlinkmode(gchar *buf, guint16 value)
2541{
2542 int len = 0;
2543 if (value & 0x1) /* Reserved */
2544 len = g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "Reserved");
2545 if (value & 0x2) /* Ethernet */
2546 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%sEthernet", (len ? ", " : ""));
2547 if (value & 0x4) /* STL */
2548 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%sSTL", (len ? ", " : ""));
2549 if (!len)
2550 g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "No State Change");
2551}
2552static void cf_opa_mad_portltpcrcmode(gchar *buf, guint16 value)
2553{
2554 int len = 0;
2555 if (value & 0x1) /* 14-bit */
2556 len = g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "14-bit");
2557 if (value & 0x2) /* 16-bit */
2558 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%s16-bit", (len ? ", " : ""));
2559 if (value & 0x4) /* 48-bit */
2560 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%s48-bit overlapping", (len ? ", " : ""));
2561 if (value & 0x8) /* 12 to 16 bit per lane */
2562 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%s[12,16]-bit per lane", (len ? ", " : ""));
2563 if (len)
2564 g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, " LTP CRC Mode");
2565 else
2566 g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "No State Change");
2567}
2568static void cf_opa_mad_packetformat(gchar *buf, guint16 value)
2569{
2570 int len = 0;
2571 if (value & 0x1) /* 8B */
2572 len = g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "8B");
2573 if (value & 0x2) /* 9B */
2574 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%s9B", (len ? ", " : ""));
2575 if (value & 0x4) /* 10B */
2576 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%s10B", (len ? ", " : ""));
2577 if (value & 0x8) /* 16B */
2578 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%s16B", (len ? ", " : ""));
2579 if (len)
2580 g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, " Format%s", (len > 4 ? "s" : ""));
2581 else
2582 g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "No State Change");
2583}
2584static void cf_opa_mad_swcongestionsetting_controlmap(gchar *buf, guint32 value)
2585{
2586 int len = 0;
2587 if (value & 0x1) /* Victim */
2588 len = g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "Victim");
2589 if (value & 0x2) /* Credit */
2590 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%sCredit", (len ? ", " : ""));
2591 if (value & 0x4) /* Thresold & PacketSize */
2592 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%sThresold & PacketSize", (len ? ", " : ""));
2593 if (value & 0x8) /* CS_threshold & CS_ReturnDelay */
2594 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%sCS_threshold & CS_ReturnDelay", (len ? ", " : ""));
2595 if (value & 0x10) /* Marking Rate */
2596 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%sMarking Rate", (len ? ", " : ""));
2597 if (!len)
2598 g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "No Valid Fields");
2599}
2600static void cf_opa_mad_32b_mask(gchar *buf, guint32 value)
2601{
2602 int len = 0;
2603 guint32 i, mask;
2604 for (i = 0, mask = value; mask && i < 32 && len < ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240; i++, mask >>= 1) {
2605 if (mask & 1) {
2606 len += g_snprintf(&buf[len], ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240 - len, "%s%u", (len ? ", " : ""), i);
2607 }
2608 }
2609 if (!len) {
2610 g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, " ");
2611 }
2612}
2613static void cf_opa_mad_computed_pct10(gchar *buf, guint16 value)
2614{
2615 g_snprintf(buf, ITEM_LABEL_LENGTH240, "%u.%01u", value / 10, value % 10);
2616}

2631static gint parse_MAD_AttributeModifier(proto_tree *MAD_tree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
2632{
2633 proto_tree *AttributeModifier_tree;
2634 proto_item *AttributeModifier_item;
2635 gint local_offset = *offset;
2636
2637 AttributeModifier_item = proto_tree_add_item(MAD_tree, hf_opa_attribute_modifier, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2638 AttributeModifier_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(AttributeModifier_item, ett_mad_attributemod);
2639
2640 switch (MAD->MgmtClass) {
2641 case SUBN_LID_ROUTED0x01:
2642 case SUBN_DIRECTED_ROUTE0x81:
2643 switch (MAD->AttributeID) {
2644 case SM_ATTR_ID_CLASS_PORT_INFO0x0001: /* Shall be 0 */
2645 case SM_ATTR_ID_NOTICE0x0002:
2646 case SM_ATTR_ID_NODE_DESCRIPTION0x0010:
2647 case SM_ATTR_ID_NODE_INFO0x0011:
2648 case SM_ATTR_ID_SWITCH_INFO0x0012:
2649 case SM_ATTR_ID_SL_SC_MAPPING_TABLE0x0017:
2650 case SM_ATTR_ID_SC_SL_MAPPING_TABLE0x0082:
2651 case SM_ATTR_ID_SM_INFO0x0020:
2652 case SM_ATTR_ID_CONGESTION_INFO0x008B:
2653 case SM_ATTR_ID_SWITCH_CONGESTION_LOG0x008C:
2654 case SM_ATTR_ID_SWITCH_CONGESTION_SETTING0x008D:
2655 case SM_ATTR_ID_HFI_CONGESTION_LOG0x008F:
2656 case SM_ATTR_ID_HFI_CONGESTION_SETTING0x0090:
2657 if (MAD->AttributeModifier)
2658 expert_add_info(NULL((void*)0), AttributeModifier_item, &ei_opa_mad_attribute_modifier_error_nonzero);
2659 break;
2660 case SM_ATTR_ID_PORT_INFO0x0015: /* NNNN NNNN 0000 0000 0000 00SA PPPP PPPP */
2661 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_Nps2AP, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2662 break;
2663 case SM_ATTR_ID_PORT_STATE_INFO0x0087: /* NNNN NNNN 0000 0000 0000 00S0 PPPP PPPP */
2664 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_NpS2P, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2665 break;
2666 case SM_ATTR_ID_LED_INFO0x0031: /* NNNN NNNN 0000 0000 0000 000A PPPP PPPP */
2667 case SM_ATTR_ID_BUFFER_CONTROL_TABLE0x008A:
2668 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_NpAP, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2669 break;
2670 case SM_ATTR_ID_PART_TABLE0x0016: /* NNNN NNNN PPPP PPPP 0000 0BBB BBBB BBBB */
2671 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_NbP2B, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2672 break;
2673 case SM_ATTR_ID_SC_SC_MAPPING_TABLE0x0081: /* NNNN NNNN 0000 00AB IIII IIII EEEE EEEE */
2674 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_NbA2B2IE, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2675 break;
2676 case SM_ATTR_ID_VL_ARBITRATION0x0018: /* NNNN NNNN SSSS SSSS 0000 000A PPPP PPPP */
2677 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_NpSAP, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2678 break;
2679 case SM_ATTR_ID_LINEAR_FWD_TABLE0x0019: /* NNNN NNNN 0000 0ABB BBBB BBBB BBBB BBBB */
2680 case SM_ATTR_ID_PORT_GROUP_FWD_TABLE0x0088:
2681 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_NbA3B3, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2682 break;
2683 case SM_ATTR_ID_MCAST_FWD_TABLE0x001B: /* NNNN NNNN PP0A BBBB BBBB BBBB BBBB BBBB */
2684 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_NbP3A4B4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2685 break;
2686 case SM_ATTR_ID_CABLE_INFO0x0032: /* 0AAA AAAA AAAA ALLL LLL0 0000 PPPP PPPP */
2687 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_A5LP, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2688 break;
2689 case SM_ATTR_ID_AGGREGATE0x0080: /* 0000 0000 0000 0000 0000 0000 NNNN NNNN */
2690 proto_tree_add_item(AttributeModifier_tree, hf_opa_attribute_modifier_N2, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2691 break;
2692 case SM_ATTR_ID_SC_VLR_MAPPING_TABLE0x0083: /* NNNN NNNN 0000 0000 000Y 000A PPPP PPPP */
2693 case SM_ATTR_ID_SC_VLT_MAPPING_TABLE0x0084:
2694 case SM_ATTR_ID_SC_VLNT_MAPPING_TABLE0x0085:
2695 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_NbYAP, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2696 break;
2697 case SM_ATTR_ID_SWITCH_PORT_CONGESTION_SETTING0x008E: /* NNNN NNNN 0000 0000 0000 0000 PPPP PPPP */
2698 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_NpP, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2699 break;
2700 case SM_ATTR_ID_HFI_CONGESTION_CONTROL_TABLE0x0091: /* NNNN NNNN 0000 0000 0000 0000 PPPP PPPP */
2701 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_NbP, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2702 break;
2703 case SM_ATTR_ID_PORT_GROUP_TABLE0x0089: /* NNNN NNNN PP00 0000 0000 0000 00AB BBBB */
2704 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(AttributeModifier_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _attribute_modifier_NbP3A6B5, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2705 break;
2706 default:
2707 if (MAD->AttributeModifier)
2708 expert_add_info(NULL((void*)0), AttributeModifier_item, &ei_opa_mad_attribute_modifier_error_nonzero);
2709 break;
2710 }
2711 break;
2712 case PERF0x04:
2713 switch (MAD->AttributeID) {
2714 case PM_ATTR_ID_CLASS_PORTINFO0x0001: /* 0 */
2715 if (MAD->AttributeModifier)
2716 expert_add_info(NULL((void*)0), AttributeModifier_item, &ei_opa_mad_attribute_modifier_error_nonzero);
2717 break;
2718 case PM_ATTR_ID_PORT_STATUS0x0040: /* PPPP PPPP 0000 0000 0000 0000 0000 0000 */
2719 case PM_ATTR_ID_CLEAR_PORT_STATUS0x0041:
2720 case PM_ATTR_ID_DATA_PORT_COUNTERS0x0042:
2721 case PM_ATTR_ID_ERROR_PORT_COUNTERS0x0043:
2722 proto_tree_add_item(AttributeModifier_tree, hf_opa_attribute_modifier_NP, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2723 break;
2724 case PM_ATTR_ID_ERROR_INFO0x0044:
2725 default:
2726 if (MAD->AttributeModifier)
2727 expert_add_info(NULL((void*)0), AttributeModifier_item, &ei_opa_mad_attribute_modifier_error_nonzero);
2728 break;
2729 }
2730 break;
2731 case PERFADMN0x32:
2732 case SUBNADMN0x03:
2733 default:
2734 if (MAD->AttributeModifier)
2735 expert_add_info(NULL((void*)0), AttributeModifier_item, &ei_opa_mad_attribute_modifier_error_nonzero);
2736 break;
2737 }
2738 return local_offset += 4;
Although the value stored to 'local_offset' is used in the enclosing expression, the value is never actually read from 'local_offset'
2739}
2740/* Parse the common MAD Header */
2741static gboolean parse_MAD_Common(proto_tree *parentTree, packet_info *pinfo, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
2742{
2743 gint local_offset = *offset;
2744 proto_item *MAD_header_item;
2745 proto_tree *MAD_header_tree;
2746 proto_item *MAD_Status_item;
2747
2748 if (MAD == NULL((void*)0)) {
2749 return FALSE(0);
2750 }
2751
2752 /* Get the Management Class to decide between LID Routed and Direct Route */
2753
2754 /* Populate the Dissector Tree */
2755 MAD_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_mad, tvb, local_offset, 24, ENC_NA0x00000000);
2756 MAD_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(MAD_header_item, ett_mad);
2757
2758 proto_tree_add_item(MAD_header_tree, hf_opa_mad_base_version, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2759 MAD->BaseVersion = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset);
2760 local_offset += 1;
2761 proto_tree_add_item(MAD_header_tree, hf_opa_mad_mgmt_class, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2762 MAD->MgmtClass = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset);
2763 local_offset += 1;
2764 proto_tree_add_item(MAD_header_tree, hf_opa_mad_class_version, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2765 MAD->ClassVersion = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset);
2766 local_offset += 1;
2767 proto_tree_add_item(MAD_header_tree, hf_opa_mad_method, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2768 MAD->Method = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset);
2769 local_offset += 1;
2770 if (MAD->MgmtClass == SUBN_DIRECTED_ROUTE0x81) {
2771 proto_tree_add_item(MAD_header_tree, hf_opa_mad_status_DR_D, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2772 MAD_Status_item = proto_tree_add_item(MAD_header_tree, hf_opa_mad_status_DR_status, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2773 MAD->Status = tvb_get_ntohs(tvb, local_offset);
2774 local_offset += 2;
2775 if (MAD->Status & 0x7FFF) {
2776 proto_item_append_text(MAD_header_item, " Error: 0x%04x", MAD->Status & 0x7FFF);
2777 expert_add_info_format(pinfo, MAD_Status_item, &ei_opa_mad_error,
2778 "Mad Status Error (0x%04x)", MAD->Status & 0x7FFF);
2779 }
2780 proto_tree_add_item(MAD_header_tree, hf_opa_mad_status_DR_Hop_Pointer, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2781 MAD->HopPointer = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset);
2782 local_offset += 1;
2783 proto_tree_add_item(MAD_header_tree, hf_opa_mad_status_DR_Hop_Count, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2784 MAD->HopCount = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset);
2785 local_offset += 1;
2786 } else {
2787 MAD_Status_item = proto_tree_add_bitmask(MAD_header_tree, tvb, local_offset,
2788 hf_opa_mad_status, ett_mad_status, _mad_status, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2789 MAD->Status = tvb_get_ntohs(tvb, local_offset);
2790 local_offset += 2;
2791 if (MAD->Status) {
2792 proto_item_append_text(MAD_header_item, " Error: 0x%04x", MAD->Status);
2793 expert_add_info_format(pinfo, MAD_Status_item, &ei_opa_mad_error,
2794 "Mad Status Error (0x%04x)", MAD->Status);
2795 }
2796 proto_tree_add_item(MAD_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2797 local_offset += 2;
2798 }
2799 proto_tree_add_item(MAD_header_tree, hf_opa_mad_transaction_id, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2800 MAD->TransactionID = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset);
2801 local_offset += 8;
2802 proto_tree_add_item(MAD_header_tree, hf_opa_mad_attribute_id, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2803 MAD->AttributeID = tvb_get_ntohs(tvb, local_offset);
2804 local_offset += 2;
2805 proto_tree_add_item(MAD_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2806 local_offset += 2;
2807
2808 MAD->AttributeModifier = tvb_get_ntohl(tvb, local_offset);
2809 *offset = parse_MAD_AttributeModifier(MAD_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
2810
2811 return TRUE(!(0));
2812}
2813/* Parse the RMPP (Reliable Multi-Packet Transaction Protocol) */
2814static gboolean parse_RMPP(proto_tree *parentTree, packet_info *pinfo, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, RMPP_t *RMPP)
2815{
2816 gint local_offset = *offset;
2817 proto_item *RMPP_header_item;
2818 proto_item *RMPP_type_item;
2819 proto_item *RMPP_segment_number_item;
2820 proto_tree *RMPP_header_tree;
2821
2822 RMPP_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_rmpp, tvb, local_offset, 12, ENC_NA0x00000000);
2823 RMPP_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(RMPP_header_item, ett_rmpp);
2824
2825 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_version, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2826 RMPP->Version = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset);
2827 local_offset += 1;
2828
2829 RMPP_type_item = proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_type, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2830 RMPP->Type = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset);
2831 local_offset += 1;
2832 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_r_resp_time, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2833 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_flags_last, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2834 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_flags_first, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2835 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_flags_active, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2836 RMPP->resptime_flags = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset);
2837 local_offset += 1;
2838
2839 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_status, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2840 RMPP->Status = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset);
2841 local_offset += 1;
2842
2843 if (!(RMPP->resptime_flags & RMPP_FLAG_ACTIVE_MASK0x01) && RMPP->Type == RMPP_ILLEGAL0) {
2844 proto_item_set_text(RMPP_header_item, "%s%s", "RMPP (Empty)", " - Reliable Multi-Packet Transaction Protocol");
2845 proto_item_append_text(RMPP_type_item, " %s", "RMPP (Empty)");
2846 } else {
2847 proto_item_set_text(RMPP_header_item, "%s%s", val_to_str(RMPP->Type, RMPP_Packet_Types, "RMPP (Reserved 0x%02x)"), " - Reliable Multi-Packet Transaction Protocol");
2848 proto_item_append_text(RMPP_type_item, " %s", val_to_str(RMPP->Type, RMPP_Packet_Types, "RMPP (Reserved 0x%02x)"));
2849 }
2850
2851 RMPP->PayloadLength = 0;
2852
2853 switch (RMPP->Type) {
2854 case RMPP_ILLEGAL0:
2855 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_data1, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2856 local_offset += 4;
2857 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_data2, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2858 local_offset += 4;
2859 break;
2860 case RMPP_DATA1:
2861 RMPP_segment_number_item = proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_segment_number, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2862 RMPP->SegmentNumber = tvb_get_ntohl(tvb, local_offset);
2863 if (RMPP->SegmentNumber > 1) {
2864 expert_add_info_format(pinfo, RMPP_segment_number_item, &ei_opa_rmpp_undecoded,
2865 "Parsing Disabled for RMPP Data Segments greater than 1 (%u)", RMPP->SegmentNumber);
2866 }
2867 local_offset += 4;
2868 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_payload_length32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2869 RMPP->PayloadLength = tvb_get_ntohl(tvb, local_offset);
2870 local_offset += 4;
2871 break;
2872 case RMPP_ACK2:
2873 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_segment_number, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2874 local_offset += 4;
2875 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_rmpp_new_window_last, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
2876 local_offset += 4;
2877 break;
2878 case RMPP_STOP3:
2879 case RMPP_ABORT4:
2880 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_NA0x00000000);
2881 local_offset += 4;
2882 proto_tree_add_item(RMPP_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_NA0x00000000);
2883 local_offset += 4;
2884 break;
2885 default:
2886 return FALSE(0);
2887 }
2888 *offset = local_offset;
2889 return TRUE(!(0));
2890}

3031/* Parse NoticesAndTraps Attribute */
3032static gint parse_NoticesAndTraps(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset)
3033{
3034 gint local_offset = *offset;
3035 proto_item *NoticesAndTraps_header_item;

3049 local_offset += 1;

3052 local_offset += 3;

3054 local_offset += 2;

3057 local_offset += 3;
3058 proto_tree_add_item(NoticesAndTraps_header_tree, hf_opa_Notice_DeviceID, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3059 local_offset += 2;
3060 }

3661
3662 /* Replay Depth */
3663 proto_tree_add_item(PortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_PortInfo_ReplayDepth_BufferDepth, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3664 local_offset += 1;
3665 proto_tree_add_item(PortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_PortInfo_ReplayDepth_WireDepth, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3666 local_offset += 1;
3667
3668 /* PortNeighborMode */
3669 proto_tree_add_item(PortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_PortInfo_PortNeighborMode_reserved, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3670 proto_tree_add_item(PortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_PortInfo_PortNeighborMode_MgmtAllowed, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3671 proto_tree_add_item(PortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_PortInfo_PortNeighborMode_NeighborFWAuthenBypass, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3672 proto_tree_add_item(PortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_PortInfo_PortNeighborMode_NeighborNodeType, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3673 local_offset += 1;
3674
3675 /* MTU */
3676 proto_tree_add_item(PortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_PortInfo_MTU_reserved, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3677 proto_tree_add_item(PortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_PortInfo_MTU_Cap, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3678 local_offset += 1;
3679
3680 proto_tree_add_item(PortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_PortInfo_Resp_reserved, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3681 proto_tree_add_item(PortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_PortInfo_Resp_TimeValue, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3682 local_offset += 1;
3683
3684 proto_tree_add_item(PortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_PortInfo_LocalPortNum, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3685 local_offset += 1;
3686
3687 proto_tree_add_item(PortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3688 local_offset += 2;
3689 /* 8 Byte Padding offset */
3690 local_offset += 8 - (242 % 8);
3691 }
3692
3693 return local_offset;
3694}

3696/* Parse PortStateInfo Attribute */
3697static gint parse_PortStateInfo(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
3698{
3699 gint local_offset = *offset;
3700 proto_item *PortStates_header_item;
3701 proto_tree *PortStates_header_tree;
3702 guint i, Num_ports, Port_num;
3703
3704 if (!parentTree || MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01 || MAD->Method == METHOD_GETTABLE0x12)
3705 return *offset;
3706
3707 Num_ports = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0xFF000000) >> 24;
3708 Port_num = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0x000000FF);
3709
3710 for (i = Port_num; i < Port_num + Num_ports; i++) {
3711 PortStates_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_PortStates, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_NA0x00000000);
3712 proto_item_set_text(PortStates_header_item, "Port Sate Info on Port %d", i);
3713 PortStates_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(PortStates_header_item, ett_portstates);
3714
3715 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(PortStates_header_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4,
3716 _PortStates, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3717 local_offset += 4;
3718
3719 proto_tree_add_item(PortStates_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStates_LinkWidthDowngradeTxActive, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3720 local_offset += 2;
3721 proto_tree_add_item(PortStates_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStates_LinkWidthDowngradeRxActive, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3722 local_offset += 2;
3723 }
3724
3725 return local_offset;
3726}

3728/* Parse P_KeyTable Attribute */
3729static gint parse_P_KeyTable(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
3730{
3731 gint local_offset = *offset;
3732 proto_item *P_KeyTable_header_item;
3733 proto_tree *P_KeyTable_header_tree;
3734 proto_tree *tempBlock_tree;
3735 proto_item *tempItemLow;
3736 proto_item *tempItemHigh;
3737 guint i, b, Num_blocks, Block_num/*, Port_num*/;
3738
3739 if (!parentTree || MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01 || MAD->Method == METHOD_GETTABLE0x12)
3740 return *offset;
3741
3742 if (MAD->MgmtClass == SUBNADMN0x03) {
3743 Num_blocks = 1;
3744 Block_num = tvb_get_ntohs(tvb, local_offset - 4);
3745 /*Port_num = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset - 2);*/
3746 } else {
3747 Num_blocks = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0xFF000000) >> 24;
3748 Block_num = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0x000007FF);
3749 /*Port_num = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0x00FF0000) >> 16;*/
3750 }

3754
3755 for (b = Block_num; b < Block_num + Num_blocks; b++) {

3757 ett_pkeytable_block, NULL((void*)0), "PKey Table Block %u", b);
3758
3759 for (i = 0; i < 32; i++) {

3761 tempItemLow = proto_tree_add_item(tempBlock_tree, hf_opa_P_KeyTable_P_KeyBase, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3762 local_offset += 2;
3763 proto_item_prepend_text(tempItemHigh, "%3u: ", i);
3764 proto_item_prepend_text(tempItemLow, " ");
3765 }
3766 }
3767 return local_offset;
3768}

3797/* Parse SCtoSC Mapping Table Attribute */
3798static gint parse_SCMappingTable(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
3799{
3800 gint local_offset = *offset;
3801 proto_item *SCtoSCMappingTable_header_item;
3802 proto_tree *SCtoSCMappingTable_header_tree;
3803 proto_item *tempItemHigh;
3804 proto_item *tempItemLow;
3805 proto_tree *tempBlock_tree;
3806 guint i, b, i_block, e_block, Num_blocks, Block_num;
3807 gboolean A, B;
3808
3809 if (!parentTree || MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01 || MAD->Method == METHOD_GETTABLE0x12)
3810 return *offset;
3811
3812 if (MAD->MgmtClass == SUBNADMN0x03) {
3813 Num_blocks = 1;
3814 A = FALSE(0);
3815 B = FALSE(0);
3816 i_block = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset - 4);
3817 e_block = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset - 3);
3818 Block_num = e_block;
3819 } else {
3820 Num_blocks = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0xFF000000) >> 24;
3821 A = (gboolean)((MAD->AttributeModifier & 0x00020000) >> 17);
3822 B = (gboolean)((MAD->AttributeModifier & 0x00010000) >> 16);
3823 i_block = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0x0000FF00) >> 8;
3824 e_block = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0x000000FF);
3825 Block_num = (B ? i_block : e_block);
3826 }
3827
3828 SCtoSCMappingTable_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_SCtoSCMappingTable, tvb, local_offset, 32 * (A ? 1 : Num_blocks), ENC_NA0x00000000);
3829 SCtoSCMappingTable_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(SCtoSCMappingTable_header_item, ett_sctoscmapping);
3830
3831 for (b = Block_num; b < (Block_num + Num_blocks); b++) {
3832 tempBlock_tree = proto_tree_add_subtree_format(SCtoSCMappingTable_header_tree, tvb, local_offset, 32,
3833 ett_sctoscmapping_block, NULL((void*)0), "SC to SC Mapping Table for InPort %u, OutPort %u", (B ? b : i_block), (B ? e_block : b));
3834
3835 for (i = 0; i < 32; i++) {
3836 tempItemHigh = proto_tree_add_item(tempBlock_tree, hf_opa_SCtoSCMappingTable_SCtoSC_HighBits, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3837 proto_item_prepend_text(tempItemHigh, "%3u: ", i);
3838 tempItemLow = proto_tree_add_item(tempBlock_tree, hf_opa_SCtoSCMappingTable_SCtoSC_LowBits, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3839 proto_item_prepend_text(tempItemLow, " ");
3840 local_offset += 1;
3841 }
3842 if (A || B)
3843 break;
3844 }
3845
3846 return local_offset;
3847}

3922/* Parse VLArbitrationTable Attribute */
3923static gint parse_VLArbitrationTable(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
3924{
3925 gint local_offset = *offset;
3926 proto_item *VLArbitrationTable_header_item;
3927 proto_tree * VLArbitrationTable_header_tree,*VLArbitrationTable_port_tree;
3928 proto_item *tempItemHigh;
3929 proto_item *tempItemLow;
3930 proto_item *tempItem;
3931 guint i, p, Section, Num_ports, Port_num;
3932 gboolean All;
3933 const gchar *TableType;
3934
3935 if (!parentTree || MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01 || MAD->Method == METHOD_GETTABLE0x12)
3936 return *offset;
3937
3938 if (MAD->MgmtClass == SUBNADMN0x03) {
3939 Num_ports = 1;
3940 Section = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset - 3);
3941 Port_num = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset - 4);
3942 All = FALSE(0);
3943 } else {
3944 Num_ports = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0xFF000000) >> 24;
3945 Section = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0x00FF0000) >> 16;
3946 All = (gboolean)((MAD->AttributeModifier & 0x00000100) >> 8);
3947 Port_num = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0x000000FF);
3948 }
3949 TableType = val_to_str_const(Section, MADAttrModSectionVLarb_short, "Reserved");
3950
3951 VLArbitrationTable_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_VLArbitrationTable, tvb, local_offset, 256 * (All ? 1 : Num_ports), ENC_NA0x00000000);
3952 VLArbitrationTable_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(VLArbitrationTable_header_item, ett_vlarbitrationtable);
3953
3954 for (p = Port_num; p < (Port_num + (All ? 1 : Num_ports)); p++) {
3955 VLArbitrationTable_port_tree = proto_tree_add_subtree_format(VLArbitrationTable_header_tree, tvb, local_offset, 256,
3956 ett_vlarbitrationtable_port, NULL((void*)0), "%s VL Arbitration Table on Port %u", TableType, p);
3957
3958 if (Section < 3) {
3959 for (i = 0; i < 128; i++) {
3960 tempItemHigh = proto_tree_add_item(VLArbitrationTable_port_tree, hf_opa_VLArbitrationTable_reserved, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3961 proto_item_prepend_text(tempItemHigh, "%3u: ", i);
3962 tempItemLow = proto_tree_add_item(VLArbitrationTable_port_tree, hf_opa_VLArbitrationTable_VL, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3963 proto_item_prepend_text(tempItemLow, " ");
3964 local_offset += 1;
3965
3966 tempItem = proto_tree_add_item(VLArbitrationTable_port_tree, hf_opa_VLArbitrationTable_Weight, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3967 local_offset += 1;
3968 proto_item_prepend_text(tempItem, " ");
3969 }
3970 } else if (Section == 3) {
3971 for (i = 0; i < 32; i++) {
3972 tempItemLow = proto_tree_add_item(VLArbitrationTable_port_tree, hf_opa_VLArbitrationTable_Matrix, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
3973 local_offset += 4;
3974 proto_item_prepend_text(tempItemLow, "%3u: ", i);
3975 }
3976 local_offset += 128;
3977 } else {
3978 local_offset += 256;
3979 }
3980 }
3981 return local_offset;
3982}

4124 }

4132
4133 for (i = 0; i < 8; i++) {
4134 tempItemLow = proto_tree_add_item(tempBlock_tree, hf_opa_PortGroupTable_PortMask, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);

4452{

4460 return *offset;

4544/* Parse HFICongestionControlTable Attribute*/
4545static gint parse_HFICongestionControlTable(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
4546{
4547 gint local_offset = *offset;
4548 proto_item *HFICongestionControlTable_header_item;
4549 proto_tree *HFICongestionControlTable_header_tree;
4550 proto_item *tempItem;
4551 proto_tree *tempBlock_tree;
4552 guint b, i, Num_blocks, Block_Num;
4553
4554 if (!parentTree || MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01 || MAD->Method == METHOD_GETTABLE0x12)
4555 return *offset;
4556
4557 if (MAD->MgmtClass == SUBNADMN0x03) {
4558 Num_blocks = 1;
4559 Block_Num = tvb_get_ntohs(tvb, local_offset - 4);
4560 } else { /* SM LID and SM DR */
4561 Num_blocks = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0xFF000000) >> 24;
4562 Block_Num = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0x000000FF);
4563 }
4564
4565 HFICongestionControlTable_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_HFICongestionControlTable, tvb, local_offset, 2 + ((64 * 2) * Num_blocks), ENC_NA0x00000000);
4566 HFICongestionControlTable_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(HFICongestionControlTable_header_item, ett_hficongestioncontroltable);
4567
4568 proto_tree_add_item(HFICongestionControlTable_header_tree, hf_opa_HFICongestionControlTable_CCTI_Limit, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
4569 local_offset += 2;
4570 for (b = Block_Num; b < Block_Num + Num_blocks; b++) {
4571 tempBlock_tree = proto_tree_add_subtree_format(HFICongestionControlTable_header_tree, tvb, local_offset, 128,
4572 ett_hficongestioncontroltable_block, NULL((void*)0), "HFI Congestion Control Table Block %u", b);
4573
4574 for (i = 0; i < 64; i++) {
4575 tempItem = proto_tree_add_item(tempBlock_tree, hf_opa_HFICongestionControlTable_CCT_Shift, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
4576 proto_item_prepend_text(tempItem, "%3u: ", i);
4577 tempItem = proto_tree_add_item(tempBlock_tree, hf_opa_HFICongestionControlTable_CCT_Multiplier, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
4578 local_offset += 2;
4579 proto_item_prepend_text(tempItem, " ");
4580
4581 }
4582 }
4583 return local_offset;
4584}
4585/* Call appropriate parsing function */
4586static gboolean call_SUBM_Parser(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, guint *offset, MAD_t *MAD, guint16 AttributeID)
4587{
4588 proto_tree *SUBM_Attribute_header_tree = parentTree;
4589 guint local_offset = *offset;
4590
4591 if (!tvb_bytes_exist(tvb, local_offset, 8))
4592 return TRUE(!(0));
4593
4594 switch (AttributeID) {
4595 case SM_ATTR_ID_CLASS_PORT_INFO0x0001:
4596 local_offset = parse_ClassPortInfo(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4597 break;
4598 case SM_ATTR_ID_NOTICE0x0002:
4599 local_offset = parse_NoticesAndTraps(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset);
4600 break;
4601 case SM_ATTR_ID_NODE_DESCRIPTION0x0010:
4602 local_offset = parse_NodeDescription(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4603 break;
4604 case SM_ATTR_ID_NODE_INFO0x0011:
4605 local_offset = parse_NodeInfo(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4606 break;
4607 case SM_ATTR_ID_SWITCH_INFO0x0012:
4608 local_offset = parse_SwitchInfo(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4609 break;
4610 case SM_ATTR_ID_PORT_INFO0x0015:
4611 local_offset = parse_PortInfo(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4612 break;
4613 case SM_ATTR_ID_PART_TABLE0x0016:
4614 local_offset = parse_P_KeyTable(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4615 break;
4616 case SM_ATTR_ID_SL_SC_MAPPING_TABLE0x0017:
4617 local_offset = parse_SLtoSCMappingTable(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4618 break;
4619 case SM_ATTR_ID_VL_ARBITRATION0x0018:
4620 local_offset = parse_VLArbitrationTable(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4621 break;
4622 case SM_ATTR_ID_LINEAR_FWD_TABLE0x0019:
4623 local_offset = parse_LinearForwardingTable(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4624 break;
4625 case SM_ATTR_ID_MCAST_FWD_TABLE0x001B:
4626 local_offset = parse_MulticastForwardingTable(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4627 break;
4628 case SM_ATTR_ID_SM_INFO0x0020:
4629 local_offset = parse_SMInfo(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4630 break;
4631 case SM_ATTR_ID_LED_INFO0x0031:
4632 local_offset = parse_LedInfo(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4633 break;
4634 case SM_ATTR_ID_CABLE_INFO0x0032:
4635 local_offset = parse_CableInfo(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4636 break;
4637 case SM_ATTR_ID_SC_SC_MAPPING_TABLE0x0081:
4638 local_offset = parse_SCMappingTable(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4639 break;
4640 case SM_ATTR_ID_SC_SL_MAPPING_TABLE0x0082:
4641 local_offset = parse_SCtoSLMappingTable(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4642 break;
4643 case SM_ATTR_ID_SC_VLR_MAPPING_TABLE0x0083:
4644 case SM_ATTR_ID_SC_VLT_MAPPING_TABLE0x0084:
4645 case SM_ATTR_ID_SC_VLNT_MAPPING_TABLE0x0085:
4646 local_offset = parse_SCtoVLxMappingTable(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4647 break;
4648 case SM_ATTR_ID_PORT_STATE_INFO0x0087:
4649 local_offset = parse_PortStateInfo(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4650 break;
4651 case SM_ATTR_ID_PORT_GROUP_FWD_TABLE0x0088:
4652 local_offset = parse_PortGroupForwardingTable(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4653 break;
4654 case SM_ATTR_ID_PORT_GROUP_TABLE0x0089:
4655 local_offset = parse_PortGroupTable(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4656 break;
4657 case SM_ATTR_ID_BUFFER_CONTROL_TABLE0x008A:
4658 local_offset = parse_BufferControlTable(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4659 break;
4660 case SM_ATTR_ID_CONGESTION_INFO0x008B:
4661 local_offset = parse_CongestionInfo(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4662 break;
4663 case SM_ATTR_ID_SWITCH_CONGESTION_LOG0x008C:
4664 local_offset = parse_SwitchCongestionLog(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4665 break;
4666 case SM_ATTR_ID_SWITCH_CONGESTION_SETTING0x008D:
4667 local_offset = parse_SwitchCongestionSetting(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4668 break;
4669 case SM_ATTR_ID_SWITCH_PORT_CONGESTION_SETTING0x008E:
4670 local_offset = parse_SwitchPortCongestionSetting(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4671 break;
4672 case SM_ATTR_ID_HFI_CONGESTION_LOG0x008F:
4673 local_offset = parse_HFICongestionLog(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4674 break;
4675 case SM_ATTR_ID_HFI_CONGESTION_SETTING0x0090:
4676 local_offset = parse_HFICongestionSetting(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4677 break;
4678 case SM_ATTR_ID_HFI_CONGESTION_CONTROL_TABLE0x0091:
4679 local_offset = parse_HFICongestionControlTable(SUBM_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, offset, MAD);
4680 break;
4681 default:
4682 return FALSE(0);
4683 }
4684 *offset = local_offset;
4685 return TRUE(!(0));
4686}
4687
4688/* Parse Aggregate Attribute */
4689static gint parse_Aggregate(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
4690{
4691 gint i;
4692 guint requestLength;
4693 gint numAttributes;
4694 gint local_offset = *offset;
4695 gint saved_offset;
4696 guint16 LocalAttributeID = 0;
4697 gboolean AggregatError = FALSE(0);
4698 proto_item *Aggregate_header_item;
4699 proto_item *Aggregate_Length_item;
4700 proto_item *Aggregate_Error_item;
4701 proto_tree *Aggregate_header_tree;
4702
4703 if (!parentTree)
4704 return *offset;
4705
4706 numAttributes = MAD->AttributeModifier & 0x000000FF;
4707
4708 for (i = 0; i < numAttributes; i++) {
4709 requestLength = (tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset + 3) & 0x7F) * 8;
4710 if (i == numAttributes - 1 && MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01) {
4711 Aggregate_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_Aggregate, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_NA0x00000000);
4712 } else {
4713 Aggregate_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_Aggregate, tvb, local_offset, requestLength + 8, ENC_NA0x00000000);
4714 }
4715 Aggregate_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(Aggregate_header_item, ett_aggregate);
4716
4717 proto_tree_add_item(Aggregate_header_tree, hf_opa_Aggregate_AttributeID, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
4718 LocalAttributeID = tvb_get_ntohs(tvb, local_offset);
4719 local_offset += 2;
4720 proto_item_set_text(Aggregate_header_item, "Aggregate %u: %s", i + 1, val_to_str(LocalAttributeID, SUBM_Attributes, "Unknown Attribute Type! (0x%02x)"));
4721
4722 AggregatError = (gboolean)tvb_get_bits(tvb, local_offset*8, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
4723 Aggregate_Error_item = proto_tree_add_item(Aggregate_header_tree, hf_opa_Aggregate_Error, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
4724 if (AggregatError)
4725 expert_add_info(NULL((void*)0), Aggregate_Error_item, &ei_opa_aggregate_error);
4726
4727 Aggregate_Length_item = proto_tree_add_item(Aggregate_header_tree, hf_opa_Aggregate_RequestLength, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
4728 proto_item_append_text(Aggregate_Length_item, " (%u Bytes)", requestLength);
4729 local_offset += 2;
4730
4731 MAD->AttributeModifier = tvb_get_ntohl(tvb, local_offset);
4732 MAD->AttributeID = LocalAttributeID;
4733 local_offset = parse_MAD_AttributeModifier(Aggregate_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
4734 if (i == numAttributes - 1 && MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01) {
4735 /* Do Nothing */
4736 } else {
4737 saved_offset = local_offset;
4738 call_SUBM_Parser(Aggregate_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD, LocalAttributeID);
4739 if (local_offset != (saved_offset + (gint)requestLength)) {
4740 local_offset = saved_offset + (gint)requestLength;
4741 }
4742 }
4743 }
4744 return local_offset;
4745}
4746/* Parse the attribute from a Subnet Management Packet. */
4747static gboolean parse_SUBM_Attribute(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
4748{
4749 gint local_offset = *offset;
4750 if (MAD->AttributeID == SM_ATTR_ID_AGGREGATE0x0080) {
4751 *offset = parse_Aggregate(parentTree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
4752 return TRUE(!(0));
4753 } else
4754 return call_SUBM_Parser(parentTree, tvb, offset, MAD, MAD->AttributeID);
4755}
4756/* Parse the Method from the MAD Common Header. */
4757static void label_SUBM_Method(proto_item *SubMItem, MAD_t *MAD, packet_info *pinfo)
4758{
4759 const guchar *label = val_to_str_const(MAD->Method, SUBM_Methods, "(Unknown SM Method!)");
4760 proto_item_append_text(SubMItem, " %s", label);
4761 col_append_str(pinfo->cinfo, COL_INFO, label);
4762}
4763/* Parse the Attribute from the MAD Common Header */
4764static void label_SUBM_Attribute(proto_item *SubMItem, MAD_t *MAD, packet_info *pinfo)
4765{
4766 const guchar *label = val_to_str_const(MAD->AttributeID, SUBM_Attributes, "Attribute (Unknown SM Attribute!)");
4767 proto_item_append_text(SubMItem, "%s", &label[11]);
4768 col_append_str(pinfo->cinfo, COL_INFO, &label[11]);
4769}
4770/* Parse Subnet Management (LID Routed) */
4771static void parse_SUBN_LID_ROUTED(proto_tree *parentTree, packet_info *pinfo, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset)
4772{
4773 MAD_t MAD;
4774 gint local_offset;
4775 proto_item *SM_LID_header_item;
4776 proto_tree *SM_LID_header_tree;
4777
4778 if (!parse_MAD_Common(parentTree, pinfo, tvb, offset, &MAD)) {
4779 return;
4780 }
4781 local_offset = *offset;
4782
4783 SM_LID_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_sm_lid, tvb, local_offset, -1, ENC_NA0x00000000);
4784 SM_LID_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(SM_LID_header_item, ett_sm_lid);
4785
4786 proto_tree_add_item(SM_LID_header_tree, hf_opa_sm_m_key, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
4787 local_offset += 8;
4788
4789 label_SUBM_Method(SM_LID_header_item, &MAD, pinfo);
4790 label_SUBM_Attribute(SM_LID_header_item, &MAD, pinfo);
4791
4792 *offset = local_offset;
4793 if (!pref_parse_on_mad_status_error && MAD.Status) {
4794 local_offset += tvb_captured_length_remaining(tvb, *offset);
4795 } else if (!parse_SUBM_Attribute(SM_LID_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, &MAD)) {
4796 expert_add_info_format(pinfo, NULL((void*)0), &ei_opa_mad_no_attribute_dissector,
4797 "Attribute Dissector Not Implemented (0x%x)", MAD.AttributeID);
4798 local_offset += tvb_captured_length_remaining(tvb, *offset);
4799 }
4800 *offset = local_offset;
4801}
4802
4803/* Parse Subnet Management (Directed Route) */
4804static void parse_SUBN_DIRECTED_ROUTE(proto_tree *parentTree, packet_info *pinfo, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset)
4805{
4806 MAD_t MAD;
4807 gint local_offset;
4808 proto_item *SM_DR_header_item;
4809 proto_tree *SM_DR_header_tree;
4810
4811 if (!parse_MAD_Common(parentTree, pinfo, tvb, offset, &MAD)) {
4812 return;
4813 }
4814 local_offset = *offset;
4815
4816 SM_DR_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_sm_dr, tvb, local_offset, -1, ENC_NA0x00000000);
4817 SM_DR_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(SM_DR_header_item, ett_sm_dr);
4818
4819 proto_tree_add_item(SM_DR_header_item, hf_opa_sm_m_key, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
4820 local_offset += 8;
4821
4822 label_SUBM_Method(SM_DR_header_item, &MAD, pinfo);
4823 label_SUBM_Attribute(SM_DR_header_item, &MAD, pinfo);
4824
4825 proto_tree_add_item(SM_DR_header_tree, hf_opa_sm_dr_slid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
4826 local_offset += 4;
4827 proto_tree_add_item(SM_DR_header_tree, hf_opa_sm_dr_dlid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
4828 local_offset += 4;
4829 proto_tree_add_item(SM_DR_header_tree, hf_opa_sm_dr_initial_path, tvb, local_offset, 64, ENC_NA0x00000000);
4830 local_offset += 64;
4831 proto_tree_add_item(SM_DR_header_tree, hf_opa_sm_dr_return_path, tvb, local_offset, 64, ENC_NA0x00000000);
4832 local_offset += 64;
4833 proto_tree_add_item(SM_DR_header_tree, hf_opa_sm_dr_reserved64, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_NA0x00000000);
4834 local_offset += 8;
4835 *offset = local_offset;
4836 if (!pref_parse_on_mad_status_error && (MAD.Status & 0x7FFF)) {
4837 local_offset += tvb_captured_length_remaining(tvb, *offset);
4838 } else if (!parse_SUBM_Attribute(SM_DR_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, &MAD)) {
4839 expert_add_info_format(pinfo, NULL((void*)0), &ei_opa_mad_no_attribute_dissector,
4840 "Attribute Dissector Not Implemented (0x%x)", MAD.AttributeID);
4841 local_offset += tvb_captured_length_remaining(tvb, *offset);
4842 return;
4843 }
4844 *offset = local_offset;
4845}
4846
4847static gint parse_PortInfoRecord(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
4848{
4849 gint local_offset = *offset;
4850 proto_tree * PortInfoRecord_LinkDownReason_tree,
4851 *PortInfoRecord_LinkDownReason_Entry_tree;
4852 gint i;
4853 local_offset = parse_PortInfo(parentTree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
