5485 proto_tree_add_item(VFInfoRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_VFInfoRecord_Rate, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5486 local_offset += 1;
5487
5488 proto_tree_add_item(VFInfoRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_VFInfoRecord_PktLifeSpecified, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5489 proto_tree_add_item(VFInfoRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_VFInfoRecord_reserved5, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5490 proto_tree_add_item(VFInfoRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_VFInfoRecord_PktLifeTimeInc, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5491 local_offset += 1;
5492
5493 proto_tree_add_item(VFInfoRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_VFInfoRecord_OptionFlags, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5494 local_offset += 1;
5495
5496 proto_tree_add_item(VFInfoRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_VFInfoRecord_BandwidthPercent, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5497 local_offset += 1;
5498
5499 proto_tree_add_item(VFInfoRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_VFInfoRecord_reserved6, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5500 proto_tree_add_item(VFInfoRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_VFInfoRecord_Priority, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5501 local_offset += 1;
5502
5503 proto_tree_add_item(VFInfoRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_VFInfoRecord_RoutingSLs, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5504 local_offset += 1;
5505
5506 proto_tree_add_item(VFInfoRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_VFInfoRecord_reserved7, tvb, local_offset, 24, ENC_NA0x00000000);
5507 local_offset += 24;
5508
5509 return local_offset;
5510}
5511static gint parse_QuarantinedNodeRecord(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
5512{
5513 gint local_offset = *offset;
5514 proto_item *QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_item;
5515 proto_tree *QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree;
5516
5517 if (!parentTree || MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01 || MAD->Method == METHOD_GETTABLE0x12)
5518 return *offset;
5519
5520 QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_QuarantinedNodeRecord, tvb, local_offset, 213, ENC_NA0x00000000);
5521 QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_item, ett_quarantinednoderecord);
5522
5523 proto_tree_add_item(QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_QuarantinedNodeRecord_TrustedLid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5524 local_offset += 4;
5525 proto_tree_add_item(QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_QuarantinedNodeRecord_TrustedPortNum, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5526 local_offset += 1;
5527 proto_tree_add_item(QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved24, tvb, local_offset, 3, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5528 local_offset += 3;
5529 proto_tree_add_item(QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_QuarantinedNodeRecord_TrustedNodeGUID, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5530 local_offset += 8;
5531 proto_tree_add_item(QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_QuarantinedNodeRecord_TrustedNeighborNodeGUID, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5532 local_offset += 8;
5533
5534 local_offset = parse_NodeDescription(QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5535 local_offset = parse_NodeInfo(QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5536
5537 proto_tree_add_item(QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_QuarantinedNodeRecord_QuarantineReasons, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5538 local_offset += 4;
5539 proto_tree_add_item(QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_QuarantinedNodeRecord_ExpectedNodeDesc, tvb, local_offset, 64, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5540 local_offset += 64;
5541 proto_tree_add_item(QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_QuarantinedNodeRecord_ExpectedNodeGUID, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5542 local_offset += 8;
5543 proto_tree_add_item(QuarantinedNodeRecord_header_tree, hf_opa_QuarantinedNodeRecord_ExpectedPortGUID, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5544 local_offset += 8;
5545
5546 return local_offset;
5547}
5548/* Parse RID Field from Subnet Administration Packets. */
5549static void parse_RID(proto_tree *SA_header_tree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
5550{
5551 gint local_offset = *offset;
5552
5553 if (!SA_header_tree)
5554 return;
5555
5556 switch (MAD->AttributeID) {
5557 case SA_ATTR_ID_CLASS_PORT_INFO0x0001:
5558 break;
5559 case SA_ATTR_ID_NOTICE0x0002:
5560 break;
5561 case SA_ATTR_ID_NODE_RECORD0x0011: /* NodeRecord */
5562 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5563 local_offset += 4;
5564 break;
5565 case SA_ATTR_ID_PORTINFO_RECORD0x0012: /* PortInfoRecord */
5566 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_EndportLID, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5567 local_offset += 4;
5568 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_PortNum, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5569 local_offset += 1;
5570 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved8, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5571 local_offset += 1;
5572 break;
5573 case SA_ATTR_ID_SC_MAPTBL_RECORD0x0013: /* SCMappingTableRecord */
5574 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5575 local_offset += 4;
5576 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_InputPortNum, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5577 local_offset += 1;
5578 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_OutputPortNum, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5579 local_offset += 1;
5580 break;
5581 case SA_ATTR_ID_SL2SC_MAPTBL_RECORD0x0080:
5582 case SA_ATTR_ID_SC2SL_MAPTBL_RECORD0x0081:
5583 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5584 local_offset += 4;
5585 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5586 local_offset += 2;
5587 break;
5588 case SA_ATTR_ID_SC_VLNT_MAPTBL_RECORD0x0082:
5589 case SA_ATTR_ID_SC_VLT_MAPTBL_RECORD0x0083:
5590 case SA_ATTR_ID_SC_VLR_MAPTBL_RECORD0x0084:
5591 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5592 local_offset += 4;
5593 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Port, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5594 local_offset += 1;
5595 break;
5596 case SA_ATTR_ID_SWITCHINFO_RECORD0x0014: /* SwitchInfoRecord */
5597 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5598 local_offset += 4;
5599 break;
5600 case SA_ATTR_ID_LINEAR_FWDTBL_RECORD0x0015: /* LinearForwardingTableRecord */
5601 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5602 local_offset += 4;
5603 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_reserved14, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5604 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_BlockNum_18b, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5605 local_offset += 4;
5606 break;
5607 case SA_ATTR_ID_MCAST_FWDTBL_RECORD0x0017: /* MulticastForwardingTableRecord */
5608 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5609 local_offset += 4;
5610 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Position, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5611 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_reserved9, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5612 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_BlockNum_21b, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5613 local_offset += 4;
5614 break;
5615 case SA_ATTR_ID_VLARBTABLE_RECORD0x0036: /*VLArbitrationTableRecord */
5616 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5617 local_offset += 4;
5618 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_OutputPortNum, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5619 local_offset += 1;
5620 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_BlockNum_8b, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5621 local_offset += 1;
5622 break;
5623 case SA_ATTR_ID_SMINFO_RECORD0x0018: /* SMInfoRecord */
5624 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5625 local_offset += 4;
5626 break;
5627 case SA_ATTR_ID_P_KEY_TABLE_RECORD0x0033: /* P_KeyTableRecord */
5628 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5629 local_offset += 4;
5630 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_BlockNum_16b, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5631 local_offset += 2;
5632 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_PortNum, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5633 local_offset += 1;
5634 break;
5635 case SA_ATTR_ID_INFORM_INFO_RECORD0x00F3: /* InformInfoRecord */
5636 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_SubscriberLID, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_NA0x00000000);
5637 local_offset += 4;
5638 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Enum, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5639 local_offset += 2;
5640 break;
5641 case SA_ATTR_ID_LINK_RECORD0x0020: /* LinkRecord */
5642 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_FromLID, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5643 local_offset += 4;
5644 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_FromPort, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5645 local_offset += 1;
5646 break;
5647 case SA_ATTR_ID_SERVICE_RECORD0x0031: /* ServiceRecord */
5648 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_ServiceID, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5649 local_offset += 8;
5650 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_ServiceLID, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_NA0x00000000);
5651 local_offset += 4;
5652 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_ServiceP_Key, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5653 local_offset += 2;
5654 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5655 local_offset += 2;
5656 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_ServiceGID, tvb, local_offset, 16, ENC_NA0x00000000);
5657 local_offset += 16;
5658 break;
5659 case SA_ATTR_ID_PATH_RECORD0x0035: /* PathRecord */
5660 break;
5661 case SA_ATTR_ID_MCMEMBER_RECORD0x0038: /* MCMemberRecord */
5662 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_MGID, tvb, local_offset, 16, ENC_NA0x00000000);
5663 local_offset += 16;
5664 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_PortGID, tvb, local_offset, 16, ENC_NA0x00000000);
5665 local_offset += 16;
5666 break;
5667 case SA_ATTR_ID_TRACE_RECORD0x0039:
5668 break;
5669 case SA_ATTR_ID_MULTIPATH_GID_RECORD0x003A:
5670 break;
5671 case SA_ATTR_ID_MULTIPATH_GUID_RECORD0x0086:
5672 break;
5673 case SA_ATTR_ID_MULTIPATH_LID_RECORD0x0087:
5674 break;
5675 case SA_ATTR_ID_CABLE_INFO_RECORD0x0088:
5676 break;
5677 case SA_ATTR_ID_VF_INFO_RECORD0x0089:
5678 break;
5679 case SA_ATTR_ID_QUARANTINED_NODE_RECORD0x0090:
5680 break;
5681 case SA_ATTR_ID_CONGESTION_INFO_RECORD0x0091:
5682 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5683 local_offset += 4;
5684 break;
5685 case SA_ATTR_ID_SWITCH_CONG_RECORD0x0092:
5686 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5687 local_offset += 4;
5688 break;
5689 case SA_ATTR_ID_SWITCH_PORT_CONG_RECORD0x0093:
5690 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5691 local_offset += 4;
5692 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Port, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5693 local_offset += 1;
5694 break;
5695 case SA_ATTR_ID_HFI_CONG_RECORD0x0094:
5696 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5697 local_offset += 4;
5698 break;
5699 case SA_ATTR_ID_HFI_CONG_CTRL_RECORD0x0095:
5700 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5701 local_offset += 4;
5702 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_BlockNum_16b, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5703 local_offset += 2;
5704 break;
5705 case SA_ATTR_ID_BUFF_CTRL_TAB_RECORD0x008C:
5706 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Lid, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5707 local_offset += 4;
5708 proto_tree_add_item(SA_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_Port, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5709 local_offset += 1;
5710 break;
5711 case SA_ATTR_ID_FABRICINFO_RECORD0x008D:
5712 break;
5713 default:
5714 break;
5715 }
5716 *offset = local_offset;
5717}
5718/* Parse the attribute from a Subnet Administration Packet. */
5719static gboolean parse_SUBA_Attribute(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD, RMPP_t *RMPP, SA_HEADER_t *SA_HEADER)
5720{
5721 proto_tree *SUBA_Attribute_header_tree = parentTree;
5722 guint local_offset = *offset;
5723
5724 if (RMPP->Type == RMPP_ACK2 || SA_HEADER->AttributeOffset == 0)
5725 return TRUE(!(0));
5726
5727 /* Skim off the RID fields should they be present */
5728 parse_RID(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5729
5730 /* Parse the rest of the attributes */
5731 switch (MAD->AttributeID) {
5732 case SA_ATTR_ID_CLASS_PORT_INFO0x0001: /* (ClassPortInfo) */
5733 local_offset = parse_ClassPortInfo(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5734 break;
5735 case SA_ATTR_ID_NOTICE0x0002: /* (Notice) */
5736 local_offset = parse_NoticesAndTraps(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
5737 break;
5738 case SA_ATTR_ID_INFORM_INFO0x0003: /* (InformInfo) */
5739 local_offset = parse_InformInfo(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5740 break;
5741 case SA_ATTR_ID_NODE_RECORD0x0011: /* (NodeRecord) */
5742 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5743 local_offset += 4;
5744 local_offset = parse_NodeInfo(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5745 local_offset = parse_NodeDescription(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5746 break;
5747 case SA_ATTR_ID_PORTINFO_RECORD0x0012: /* (PortInfoRecord) */
5748 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5749 local_offset += 2;
5750 local_offset = parse_PortInfoRecord(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5751 break;
5752 case SA_ATTR_ID_SL2SC_MAPTBL_RECORD0x0080:
5753 local_offset = parse_SLtoSCMappingTable(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5754 break;
5755 case SA_ATTR_ID_SC_MAPTBL_RECORD0x0013:
5756 local_offset = parse_SCMappingTable(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5757 break;
5758 case SA_ATTR_ID_SC2SL_MAPTBL_RECORD0x0081:
5759 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5760 local_offset += 2;
5761 local_offset = parse_SCtoSLMappingTable(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5762 break;
5763 case SA_ATTR_ID_SC_VLNT_MAPTBL_RECORD0x0082:
5764 case SA_ATTR_ID_SC_VLT_MAPTBL_RECORD0x0083:
5765 case SA_ATTR_ID_SC_VLR_MAPTBL_RECORD0x0084:
5766 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved24, tvb, local_offset, 3, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5767 local_offset += 3;
5768 local_offset = parse_SCtoVLxMappingTable(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5769 break;
5770 case SA_ATTR_ID_SWITCHINFO_RECORD0x0014: /* (SwitchInfoRecord) */
5771 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5772 local_offset += 4;
5773 local_offset = parse_SwitchInfo(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5774 break;
5775 case SA_ATTR_ID_LINEAR_FWDTBL_RECORD0x0015: /*(LinearForwardingTableRecord) */
5776 local_offset = parse_LinearForwardingTable(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5777 break;
5778 case SA_ATTR_ID_MCAST_FWDTBL_RECORD0x0017: /* (MulticastForwardingTableRecord) */
5779 local_offset = parse_MulticastForwardingTable(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5780 break;
5781 case SA_ATTR_ID_VLARBTABLE_RECORD0x0036: /* (VLArbitrationTableRecord) */
5782 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5783 local_offset += 2;
5784 local_offset = parse_VLArbitrationTable(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5785 break;
5786 case SA_ATTR_ID_SMINFO_RECORD0x0018: /* (SMInfoRecord) */
5787 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5788 local_offset += 4;
5789 local_offset = parse_SMInfo(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5790 break;
5791 case SA_ATTR_ID_P_KEY_TABLE_RECORD0x0033: /* (P_KeyTableRecord) */
5792 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved8, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5793 local_offset += 1;
5794 local_offset = parse_P_KeyTable(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5795 break;
5796 case SA_ATTR_ID_INFORM_INFO_RECORD0x00F3: /*(InformInfoRecord) */
5797 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5798 local_offset += 2;
5799 local_offset = parse_InformInfo(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5800 break;
5801 case SA_ATTR_ID_LINK_RECORD0x0020: /* (LinkRecord) */
5802 local_offset = parse_LinkRecord(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
5803 break;
5804 case SA_ATTR_ID_SERVICE_RECORD0x0031: /*(ServiceRecord) */
5805 local_offset = parse_ServiceRecord(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
5806 break;
5807 case SA_ATTR_ID_PATH_RECORD0x0035: /* (PathRecord) */
5808 local_offset = parse_PathRecord(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
5809 break;
5810 case SA_ATTR_ID_MCMEMBER_RECORD0x0038: /* (MCMemberRecord) */
5811 local_offset = parse_MCMemberRecord(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
5812 break;
5813 case SA_ATTR_ID_TRACE_RECORD0x0039: /* (TraceRecord) */
5814 local_offset = parse_TraceRecord(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
5815 break;
5816 case SA_ATTR_ID_MULTIPATH_GID_RECORD0x003A: /* (MultiPathRecord) */
5817 local_offset = parse_MultiPathRecord_GID(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
5818 break;
5819 case SA_ATTR_ID_MULTIPATH_GUID_RECORD0x0086:
5820 local_offset = parse_MultiPathRecord_GUID(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
5821 break;
5822 case SA_ATTR_ID_MULTIPATH_LID_RECORD0x0087:
5823 local_offset = parse_MultiPathRecord_lid(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
5824 break;
5825 case SA_ATTR_ID_SERVICEASSOCIATION_RECORD0x003B: /* (ServiceAssociationRecord) */
5826 local_offset = parse_ServiceAssociationRecord(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
5827 break;
5828 case SA_ATTR_ID_PGROUP_FWDTBL_RECORD0x0085:
5829 local_offset = parse_PortGroupForwardingTable(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5830 break;
5831 case SA_ATTR_ID_CABLE_INFO_RECORD0x0088: /* (CableInfoRecord) */
5832 local_offset = parse_CableInfoRecord(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
5833 break;
5834 case SA_ATTR_ID_VF_INFO_RECORD0x0089:
5835 local_offset = parse_VFInfoRecord(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
5836 break;
5837 case SA_ATTR_ID_QUARANTINED_NODE_RECORD0x0090:
5838 local_offset = parse_QuarantinedNodeRecord(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5839 break;
5840 case SA_ATTR_ID_CONGESTION_INFO_RECORD0x0091:
5841 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5842 local_offset += 4;
5843 local_offset = parse_CongestionInfo(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5844 break;
5845 case SA_ATTR_ID_SWITCH_CONG_RECORD0x0092:
5846 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5847 local_offset += 4;
5848 local_offset = parse_SwitchCongestionSetting(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5849 break;
5850 case SA_ATTR_ID_SWITCH_PORT_CONG_RECORD0x0093:
5851 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved24, tvb, local_offset, 3, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5852 local_offset += 3;
5853 local_offset = parse_SwitchPortCongestionSetting(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5854 break;
5855 case SA_ATTR_ID_HFI_CONG_RECORD0x0094:
5856 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5857 local_offset += 4;
5858 local_offset = parse_HFICongestionSetting(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5859 break;
5860 case SA_ATTR_ID_HFI_CONG_CTRL_RECORD0x0095:
5861 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5862 local_offset += 2;
5863 local_offset = parse_HFICongestionControlTable(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5864 break;
5865 case SA_ATTR_ID_BUFF_CTRL_TAB_RECORD0x008C:
5866 proto_tree_add_item(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved24, tvb, local_offset, 3, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5867 local_offset += 3;
5868 local_offset = parse_BufferControlTable(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5869 break;
5870 case SA_ATTR_ID_FABRICINFO_RECORD0x008D:
5871 local_offset = parse_FabricInfoRecord(SUBA_Attribute_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
5872 break;
5873 default: /* (Unknown SubAdministration Attribute!) */
5874 /* We've already labeled as unknown in item construction */
5875 break;
5876 }
5877
5878 *offset = local_offset;
5879 return TRUE(!(0));
5880}
5881/* Parse the SA Method from the MAD Common Header. */
5882static void label_SUBA_Method(proto_item *SubAItem, MAD_t *MAD, packet_info *pinfo)
5883{
5884 const guchar *label = val_to_str_const(MAD->Method, SUBA_Methods, "(Unknown SA Method!)");
5885 proto_item_append_text(SubAItem, " %s", label);
5886 col_append_str(pinfo->cinfo, COL_INFO, label);
5887}
5888/* Parse the SA Attribute from the MAD Common Header */
5889static void label_SUBA_Attribute(proto_item *SubAItem, MAD_t *MAD, packet_info *pinfo)
5890{
5891 const guchar *label = val_to_str_const(MAD->AttributeID, SUBA_Attributes, "Attribute (Unknown SA Attribute!)");
5892 proto_item_append_text(SubAItem, "%s", &label[11]);
5893 col_append_str(pinfo->cinfo, COL_INFO, &label[11]);
5894}
5895/* Parse the SA_HEADER
5896* IN: parentTree to add the dissection to
5897* IN: tvb - the data buffer from wireshark
5898* IN/OUT: The current and updated offset */
5899static gboolean parse_SA_HEADER(proto_tree *parentTree, packet_info *pinfo, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD, SA_HEADER_t *SA_HEADER)
5900{
5901 gint local_offset = *offset;
5902 proto_item *SA_HEADER_header_item;
5903 proto_tree *SA_HEADER_header_tree;
5904
5905 SA_HEADER_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_sa, tvb, local_offset, 20, ENC_NA0x00000000);
5906 SA_HEADER_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(SA_HEADER_header_item, ett_sa);
5907
5908 SA_HEADER->SM_Key = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset);
5909 proto_tree_add_item(SA_HEADER_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_sm_key, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5910 local_offset += 8;
5911 SA_HEADER->AttributeOffset = tvb_get_ntohs(tvb, local_offset);
5912 proto_tree_add_item(SA_HEADER_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_attribute_offset, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5913 local_offset += 2;
5914 SA_HEADER->Reserved = tvb_get_ntohs(tvb, local_offset);
5915 proto_tree_add_item(SA_HEADER_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5916 local_offset += 2;
5917 SA_HEADER->ComponentMask = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset);
5918 proto_tree_add_item(SA_HEADER_header_tree, hf_opa_sa_component_mask, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5919 local_offset += 8;
5920
5921 label_SUBA_Method(SA_HEADER_header_item, MAD, pinfo);
5922 label_SUBA_Attribute(SA_HEADER_header_item, MAD, pinfo);
5923
5924 *offset = local_offset;
5925 return TRUE(!(0));
5926}
5927/* Parse Subnet Administration */
5928static void parse_SUBNADMN(proto_tree *parentTree, packet_info *pinfo, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset)
5929{
5930 MAD_t MAD;
5931 RMPP_t RMPP;
5932 SA_HEADER_t SA_HEADER;
5933
5934 if (!parse_MAD_Common(parentTree, pinfo, tvb, offset, &MAD)) {
5935 return;
5936 }
5937 if (!parse_RMPP(parentTree, pinfo, tvb, offset, &RMPP)) {
5938 return;
5939 }
5940 if (!parse_SA_HEADER(parentTree, pinfo, tvb, offset, &MAD, &SA_HEADER)) {
5941 return;
5942 }
5943 if ((!pref_parse_on_mad_status_error && MAD.Status) ||
5944 RMPP.Type == RMPP_ACK2 || SA_HEADER.AttributeOffset == 0 ||
5945 (RMPP.Type == RMPP_DATA1 && RMPP.SegmentNumber != 1)) {
5946 *offset += tvb_captured_length_remaining(tvb, *offset);
5947 return;
5948 }
5949 if (!parse_SUBA_Attribute(parentTree, tvb, offset, &MAD, &RMPP, &SA_HEADER)) {
5950 expert_add_info_format(pinfo, NULL((void*)0), &ei_opa_mad_no_attribute_dissector,
5951 "Attribute Dissector Not Implemented (0x%x)", MAD.AttributeID);
5952 *offset += tvb_captured_length_remaining(tvb, *offset);
5953 return;
5954 }
5955}
5956
5957/* Parse PortStatus MAD from the Performance management class. */
5958static gint parse_PortStatus(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
5959{
5960 proto_item *PortStatus_header_item;
5961 proto_tree *PortStatus_header_tree;
5962 proto_tree *PortStatus_VL_tree;
5963 gint local_offset = *offset;
5964 guint32 VLSelectMask;
5965 guint i, VLs;
5966 guint32 vlSelMskTmp;
5967
5968 if (!parentTree)
5969 return *offset;
5970
5971 VLSelectMask = tvb_get_ntohl(tvb, local_offset + 4);
5972 for (i = 0, VLs = 0, vlSelMskTmp = VLSelectMask; vlSelMskTmp && i < 32 && vlSelMskTmp; i++, vlSelMskTmp >>= 1) {
5973 VLs = VLs + (vlSelMskTmp & 0x1);
5974 }
5975
5976 if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01) { /* Get() */
5977 PortStatus_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_PortStatus, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_NA0x00000000);
5978 } else if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET_RESP0x81) { /* GetResp(): */
5979 PortStatus_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_PortStatus, tvb, local_offset, 208 + VLs * 112, ENC_NA0x00000000);
5980 } else {
5981 return *offset;
5982 }
5983 PortStatus_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(PortStatus_header_item, ett_portstatus);
5984
5985 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortNumber, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5986 local_offset += 1;
5987 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved24, tvb, local_offset, 3, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5988 local_offset += 3;
5989
5990 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_VLSelectMask, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5991 local_offset += 4;
5992
5993 if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01)
5994 return local_offset;
5995
5996 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortXmitData, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5997 local_offset += 8;
5998 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortRcvData, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
5999 local_offset += 8;
6000 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortXmitPkts, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6001 local_offset += 8;
6002 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortRcvPkts, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6003 local_offset += 8;
6004
6005 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortMulticastXmitPkts, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6006 local_offset += 8;
6007 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortMulticastRcvPkts, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6008 local_offset += 8;
6009 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortXmitWait, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6010 local_offset += 8;
6011 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_SwPortCongestion, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6012 local_offset += 8;
6013 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortRcvFECN, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6014 local_offset += 8;
6015
6016 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortRcvBECN, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6017 local_offset += 8;
6018 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortXmitTimeCong, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6019 local_offset += 8;
6020 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortXmitWastedBW, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6021 local_offset += 8;
6022 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortXmitWaitData, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6023 local_offset += 8;
6024 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortRcvBubble, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6025 local_offset += 8;
6026
6027 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortMarkFECN, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6028 local_offset += 8;
6029 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortRcvConstraintErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6030 local_offset += 8;
6031 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortRcvSwitchRelayErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6032 local_offset += 8;
6033 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortXmitDiscards, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6034 local_offset += 8;
6035 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortXmitConstraintErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6036 local_offset += 8;
6037
6038 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortRcvRemotePhysicalErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6039 local_offset += 8;
6040 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_LocalLinkIntegrityErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6041 local_offset += 8;
6042 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortRcvErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6043 local_offset += 8;
6044 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_ExcessiveBufferOverruns, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6045 local_offset += 8;
6046 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_FMConfigErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6047 local_offset += 8;
6048
6049 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_LinkErrorRecovery, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6050 local_offset += 4;
6051 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_LinkDowned, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6052 local_offset += 4;
6053
6054 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_UncorrectableErrors, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6055 local_offset += 1;
6056 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_reserved, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6057 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_LinkQualityIndicator, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6058 local_offset += 1;
6059
6060 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6061 local_offset += 2;
6062 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6063 local_offset += 4;
6064
6065 for (i = 0, vlSelMskTmp = VLSelectMask; vlSelMskTmp && i < 32; i++, vlSelMskTmp >>= 1) {
6066 if (vlSelMskTmp & 0x1) {
6067 PortStatus_VL_tree = proto_tree_add_subtree_format(PortStatus_header_tree, tvb, local_offset, 112,
6068 ett_portstatus_vl, NULL((void*)0), "VL %u", i);
6069
6070 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLXmitData, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6071 local_offset += 8;
6072 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLRcvData, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6073 local_offset += 8;
6074 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLXmitPkts, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6075 local_offset += 8;
6076 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLRcvPkts, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6077 local_offset += 8;
6078 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLXmitWait, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6079 local_offset += 8;
6080
6081 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_SwPortVLCongestion, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6082 local_offset += 8;
6083 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLRcvFECN, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6084 local_offset += 8;
6085 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLRcvBECN, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6086 local_offset += 8;
6087 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLXmitTimeCong, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6088 local_offset += 8;
6089 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLXmitWastedBW, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6090 local_offset += 8;
6091
6092 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLXmitWaitData, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6093 local_offset += 8;
6094 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLRcvBubble, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6095 local_offset += 8;
6096 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLMarkFECN, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6097 local_offset += 8;
6098 proto_tree_add_item(PortStatus_VL_tree, hf_opa_PortStatus_PortVLXmitDiscards, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6099 local_offset += 8;
6100 }
6101 }
6102 return local_offset;
6103}
6104
6105/* Parse ClearPortStatus MAD from the Performance management class.*/
6106static gint parse_ClearPortStatus(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
6107{
6108 proto_item *ClearPortStatus_header_item;
6109 proto_tree *ClearPortStatus_header_tree;
6110 proto_item *ClearPortStatus_PortSelectMask_item;
6111 gint local_offset = *offset;
6112 guint64 PortSelectMask[4];
6113 guint64 PortSelectMaskTemp;
6114 guint i, j;
6115 guint PortsOffset = 0;
6116
6117 if (!parentTree)
6118 return *offset;
6119
6120 if (MAD->Method == METHOD_SET0x02 || MAD->Method == METHOD_GET_RESP0x81) { /* Only Set()/GetResp() is supported. */
6121 ClearPortStatus_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_ClearPortStatus, tvb, local_offset, 36, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6122 } else
6123 return *offset;
6124
6125 ClearPortStatus_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(ClearPortStatus_header_item, ett_clearportstatus);
6126 PortSelectMask[0] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset);
6127 PortSelectMask[1] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset + 8);
6128 PortSelectMask[2] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset + 16);
6129 PortSelectMask[3] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset + 24);
6130
6131 ClearPortStatus_PortSelectMask_item = proto_tree_add_item(ClearPortStatus_header_tree, hf_opa_ClearPortStatus_PortSelectMask, tvb, local_offset, 32, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6132 for (j = 0; j < 4; j++) {
6133 for (i = 0, PortSelectMaskTemp = PortSelectMask[3 - j]; i < 64 && (PortSelectMaskTemp); i++, PortSelectMaskTemp >>= (guint64)1) {
6134 if (PortSelectMaskTemp & (guint64)0x1) {
6135 proto_item_append_text(ClearPortStatus_PortSelectMask_item, "%s%u", (PortsOffset ? ", " : " "), (i)+(j * 64));
6136 PortsOffset++;
6137 }
6138 }
6139 }
6140 local_offset += 32;
6141
6142 proto_tree_add_bitmask(ClearPortStatus_header_tree, tvb, local_offset,
6143 hf_opa_ClearPortStatus_CounterSelectMask, ett_clearportstatus_counterselectmask,
6144 _ClearPortStatus_CounterSelectMask, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6145 local_offset += 4;
6146
6147 return local_offset;
6148}
6149
6150/* Parse DataPortCounters MAD from the Performance management class.*/
6151static gint parse_DataPortCounters(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
6152{
6153 proto_item *DataPortCounters_header_item;
6154 proto_item *DataPortCounters_PortSelectMask_item;
6155 proto_tree *DataPortCounters_header_tree;
6156 proto_tree *DataPortCounters_Port_tree;
6157 proto_tree *DataPortCounters_VL_tree;
6158
6159 gint local_offset = *offset;
6160 guint32 VLSelectMask, vlSelMskTmp;
6161 guint64 PortSelectMask[4];
6162 guint64 PortSelectMaskTemp;
6163 guint VLs, i, j, p;
6164 guint PortsOffset = 0;
6165 guint Num_Ports = (MAD->AttributeModifier >> 24) & 0xFF;
6166
6167 if (!parentTree)
6168 return *offset;
6169
6170 VLSelectMask = tvb_get_ntohl(tvb, local_offset + 32);
6171 for (i = 0, VLs = 0, vlSelMskTmp = VLSelectMask; vlSelMskTmp && i < 32 && vlSelMskTmp; i++, vlSelMskTmp >>= 1) {
6172 VLs += (vlSelMskTmp & 0x1);
6173 }
6174
6175 if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01) { /* Get() */
6176 DataPortCounters_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_DataPortCounters, tvb, local_offset, 40, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6177 } else if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET_RESP0x81) { /* GetResp(): */
6178 DataPortCounters_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_DataPortCounters, tvb, local_offset, 40 + Num_Ports * (136 + VLs * 104), ENC_NA0x00000000);
6179 } else { /* Set() */
6180 return *offset;
6181 }
6182 DataPortCounters_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(DataPortCounters_header_item, ett_dataportcounters);
6183
6184 PortSelectMask[0] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset);
6185 PortSelectMask[1] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset + 8);
6186 PortSelectMask[2] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset + 16);
6187 PortSelectMask[3] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset + 24);
6188
6189 DataPortCounters_PortSelectMask_item = proto_tree_add_item(DataPortCounters_header_tree, hf_opa_DataPortCounters_PortSelectMask, tvb, local_offset, 32, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6190 for (j = 0; j < 4; j++) {
6191 for (i = 0, PortSelectMaskTemp = PortSelectMask[3 - j]; i < 64 && (PortSelectMaskTemp); i++, PortSelectMaskTemp >>= (guint64)1) {
6192 if (PortSelectMaskTemp & (guint64)0x1) {
6193 proto_item_append_text(DataPortCounters_PortSelectMask_item, "%s%u", (PortsOffset ? ", " : " "), (i)+(j * 64));
6194 PortsOffset++;
6195 }
6196 }
6197 }
6198 local_offset += 32;
6199
6200 proto_tree_add_item(DataPortCounters_header_tree, hf_opa_DataPortCounters_VLSelectMask, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6201 local_offset += 4;
6202
6203 proto_tree_add_item(DataPortCounters_header_tree, hf_opa_DataPortCounters_resolution_reserved, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6204 proto_tree_add_item(DataPortCounters_header_tree, hf_opa_DataPortCounters_LocalLinkIntegrityResolution, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6205 proto_tree_add_item(DataPortCounters_header_tree, hf_opa_DataPortCounters_LinkErrorRecoveryResolution, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6206 local_offset += 4;
6207
6208 if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01)
6209 return local_offset;
6210
6211 for (p = 0; p < Num_Ports; p++) {
6212 DataPortCounters_Port_tree = proto_tree_add_subtree_format(DataPortCounters_header_tree, tvb, local_offset, (1 + 3 + 4 + (8 * 16) + VLs * (8 * 13)),
6213 ett_dataportcounters_port, NULL((void*)0), "Port %u", tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset));
6214

6216 local_offset += 1;

6218 local_offset += 3;
6219 proto_tree_add_item(DataPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_DataPortCounters_lqi_reserved, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6220 proto_tree_add_item(DataPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_DataPortCounters_LinkQualityIndicator, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6221 local_offset += 4;
6222
6223 proto_tree_add_item(DataPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_DataPortCounters_PortXmitData, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6224 local_offset += 8;

6230 local_offset += 8;

6239 local_offset += 8;
6240 proto_tree_add_item(DataPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_DataPortCounters_PortRcvFECN, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6241 local_offset += 8;
6242

6260 if (vlSelMskTmp & 0x1) {

6263
6264 proto_tree_add_item(DataPortCounters_VL_tree, hf_opa_DataPortCounters_PortVLXmitData, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);

6292 }
6293 }
6294 }

6297
6298/* Parse ErrorPortCounters MAD from the Performance management class.*/
6299static gint parse_ErrorPortCounters(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
6300{
6301 proto_item *ErrorPortCounters_header_item;
6302 proto_item *ErrorPortCounters_PortSelectMask_item;
6303 proto_item *ErrorPortCounters_VL_item;
6304 proto_tree *ErrorPortCounters_header_tree;
6305 proto_tree *ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree;
6306
6307 gint local_offset = *offset;
6308 guint32 VLSelectMask, vlSelMskTmp;
6309 guint64 PortSelectMask[4];
6310 guint64 PortSelectMaskTemp;
6311 guint VLs, i, j, p;
6312 guint PortsOffset = 0;
6313 guint Num_Ports = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0xFF000000) >> 24;
6314
6315 if (!parentTree)
6316 return *offset;
6317
6318 VLSelectMask = tvb_get_ntohl(tvb, local_offset + 32);
6319 for (i = 0, VLs = 0, vlSelMskTmp = VLSelectMask; vlSelMskTmp && i < 32; i++, vlSelMskTmp >>= 1) {
6320 VLs += (vlSelMskTmp & 0x1);
6321 }
6322
6323 if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01) { /* Get() */
6324 ErrorPortCounters_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters, tvb, local_offset, 40, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6325 } else if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET_RESP0x81) { /* GetResp(): */
6326 ErrorPortCounters_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters, tvb, local_offset, 40 + Num_Ports * (96 + VLs * 8), ENC_NA0x00000000);
6327 } else { /* Set() */
6328 return *offset;
6329 }
6330 ErrorPortCounters_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(ErrorPortCounters_header_item, ett_errorportcounters);
6331
6332 PortSelectMask[0] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset);
6333 PortSelectMask[1] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset + 8);
6334 PortSelectMask[2] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset + 16);
6335 PortSelectMask[3] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset + 24);
6336 ErrorPortCounters_PortSelectMask_item = proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_header_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_PortSelectMask, tvb, local_offset, 32, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6337 for (j = 0; j < 4; j++) {
6338 for (i = 0, PortSelectMaskTemp = PortSelectMask[3 - j]; i < 64 && (PortSelectMaskTemp); i++, PortSelectMaskTemp >>= (guint64)1) {
6339 if (PortSelectMaskTemp & (guint64)0x1) {
6340 proto_item_append_text(ErrorPortCounters_PortSelectMask_item, "%s%u", (PortsOffset ? ", " : " "), (i)+(j * 64));
6341 PortsOffset++;
6342 }
6343 }
6344 }
6345 local_offset += 32;
6346
6347 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_header_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_VLSelectMask, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6348 local_offset += 4;
6349
6350 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6351 local_offset += 4;
6352
6353 if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01)
6354 return local_offset;
6355
6356 for (p = 0; p < Num_Ports; p++) {
6357 ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree = proto_tree_add_subtree_format(ErrorPortCounters_header_tree, tvb, local_offset, (96 + VLs * 8),
6358 ett_errorportcounters_port, NULL((void*)0), "Port %u", tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset));
6359
6360 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_PortNumber, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6361 local_offset += 1;
6362 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_reserved24, tvb, local_offset, 3, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6363 local_offset += 3;
6364 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6365 local_offset += 4;
6366 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_PortRcvConstraintErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6367 local_offset += 8;
6368 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_PortRcvSwitchRelayErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6369 local_offset += 8;
6370 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_PortXmitDiscards, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6371 local_offset += 8;
6372 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_PortXmitConstraintErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6373 local_offset += 8;
6374 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_PortRcvRemotePhysicalErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6375 local_offset += 8;
6376
6377 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_LocalLinkIntegrityErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6378 local_offset += 8;
6379 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_PortRcvErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6380 local_offset += 8;
6381 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_ExcessiveBufferOverruns, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6382 local_offset += 8;
6383 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_FMConfigErrors, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6384 local_offset += 8;
6385
6386 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_LinkErrorRecovery, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6387 local_offset += 4;
6388 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_LinkDowned, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6389 local_offset += 4;
6390
6391 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_UncorrectableErrors, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6392 local_offset += 1;
6393
6394 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_reserved24, tvb, local_offset, 3, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6395 local_offset += 3;
6396 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6397 local_offset += 4;
6398
6399 for (i = 0, vlSelMskTmp = VLSelectMask; vlSelMskTmp && i < 32; i++, vlSelMskTmp >>= 1) {
6400 if (vlSelMskTmp & 0x1) {
6401 ErrorPortCounters_VL_item = proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortCounters_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortCounters_PortVLXmitDiscards, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6402 local_offset += 8;
6403 proto_item_prepend_text(ErrorPortCounters_VL_item, "%3u: ", i);
6404 }
6405 }
6406 }
6407 return local_offset;
6408}
6409
6410/* Parse ErrorPortInfo MAD from the Performance management class.*/
6411static gint parse_ErrorPortInfo(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
6412{
6413 proto_item *ErrorPortInfo_header_item;
6414 proto_item *ErrorPortInfo_PortSelectMask_item;
6415
6416 proto_tree *ErrorPortInfo_header_tree;
6417 proto_tree *ErrorPortInfo_Port_tree;
6418 proto_tree * PortRcvErrorInfo_tree,
6419 *ExcessiveBufferOverrunInfo_tree,
6420 *PortXmitConstraintErrorInfo_tree,
6421 *PortRcvConstraintErrorInfo_tree,
6422 *PortRcvSwitchRelayErrorInfo_tree,
6423 *UncorrectableErrorInfo_tree,
6424 *FMConfigErrorInfo_tree;
6425
6426 gint local_offset = *offset;
6427 guint64 PortSelectMask[4];
6428 guint64 PortSelectMaskTemp;
6429 guint i, j, p, ErrorCode;
6430 guint PortsOffset = 0;
6431 guint Num_Ports = (MAD->AttributeModifier & 0xFF000000) >> 24;
6432
6433 if (!parentTree)
6434 return *offset;
6435
6436 if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET_RESP0x81) {
6437 ErrorPortInfo_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo, tvb, local_offset, -1, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6438 } else if (MAD->Method == METHOD_SET0x02) {
6439 ErrorPortInfo_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo, tvb, local_offset, 40, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6440 } else { /* GET */
6441 ErrorPortInfo_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo, tvb, local_offset, 32, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6442 }
6443 ErrorPortInfo_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(ErrorPortInfo_header_item, ett_errorportinfo);
6444
6445 PortSelectMask[0] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset);
6446 PortSelectMask[1] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset + 8);
6447 PortSelectMask[2] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset + 16);
6448 PortSelectMask[3] = tvb_get_ntoh64(tvb, local_offset + 24);
6449 ErrorPortInfo_PortSelectMask_item = proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortSelectMask, tvb, local_offset, 32, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6450 for (j = 0; j < 4; j++) {
6451 for (i = 0, PortSelectMaskTemp = PortSelectMask[3 - j]; i < 64 && (PortSelectMaskTemp); i++, PortSelectMaskTemp >>= (guint64)1) {
6452 if (PortSelectMaskTemp & (guint64)0x1) {
6453 proto_item_append_text(ErrorPortInfo_PortSelectMask_item, "%s%u", (PortsOffset ? ", " : " "), (i)+(j * 64));
6454 PortsOffset++;
6455 }
6456 }
6457 }
6458 local_offset += 32;
6459
6460 if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01)
6461 return local_offset;
6462 /* ErrorInfoSelectMask */
6463 proto_tree_add_bitmask_list(ErrorPortInfo_header_tree, tvb, local_offset, 4, _ErrorPortInfo_ErrorInfoSelectMask, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6464 local_offset += 4;
6465
6466 if (MAD->Method == METHOD_SET0x02
6467 /* GetResp packet from a Set operation will contain 1 zeroed port struct */
6468 || (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET_RESP0x81 && Num_Ports > 1
6469 && tvb_reported_length_remaining(tvb, local_offset) < (72 * 2)))
6470 return local_offset;
6471
6472 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortInfo_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6473 local_offset += 4;
6474 for (p = 0; p < Num_Ports; p++) {
6475 ErrorPortInfo_Port_tree = proto_tree_add_subtree_format(ErrorPortInfo_header_tree, tvb, local_offset, 72,
6476 ett_errorportinfoport, NULL((void*)0), "Port %u", tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset));
6477
6478 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortInfo_Port_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortNumber, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6479 local_offset += 1;
6480 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortInfo_Port_tree, hf_opa_reserved24, tvb, local_offset, 3, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6481 local_offset += 3;
6482 proto_tree_add_item(ErrorPortInfo_Port_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6483 local_offset += 4;
6484
6485 /* PortRcvErrorInfo */
6486 PortRcvErrorInfo_tree = proto_tree_add_subtree(ErrorPortInfo_Port_tree, tvb, local_offset, 24,
6487 ett_errorportinfo_portrcverrorinfo, NULL((void*)0), "PortRcv Error Info");
6488
6489 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortRcvErrorInfo_Status, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6490 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortRcvErrorInfo_reserved, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6491 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortRcvErrorInfo_ErrorCode, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6492 ErrorCode = tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset) & 0x0F;
6493 local_offset += 1;
6494 if (ErrorCode >= 1 && ErrorCode <= 12) {
6495 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortRcvErrorInfo_PacketFlit1, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6496 local_offset += 8;
6497 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortRcvErrorInfo_PacketFlit2, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6498 local_offset += 8;
6499 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortRcvErrorInfo_Flit1Bits, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6500 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortRcvErrorInfo_Flit2Bits, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6501 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortRcvErrorInfo_reserved2, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6502 local_offset += 1;
6503 } else if (ErrorCode == 13) {
6504 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortRcvErrorInfo_PacketBytes, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6505 local_offset += 8;
6506 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortRcvErrorInfo_FlitBits, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6507 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortRcvErrorInfo_reserved3, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6508 local_offset += 1;
6509 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_reserved64, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6510 local_offset += 8;
6511 } else {
6512 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_ErrorPortInfo_PortRcvErrorInfo_reserved4, tvb, local_offset, 17, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6513 local_offset += 17;
6514 }
6515 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_reserved16, tvb, local_offset, 2, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6516 local_offset += 2;
6517 proto_tree_add_item(PortRcvErrorInfo_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);

6649static gboolean parse_PM_Attribute(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
6650{
6651 gint local_offset = *offset;
6652
6653 switch (MAD->AttributeID) {
6654 /* Mgmt */
6655 case PA_ATTR_ID_CLASS_PORTINFO0x0001:
6656 local_offset = parse_ClassPortInfo(parentTree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
6657 break;
6658 case PM_ATTR_ID_PORT_STATUS0x0040:
6659 local_offset = parse_PortStatus(parentTree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
6660 break;
6661 case PM_ATTR_ID_CLEAR_PORT_STATUS0x0041:
6662 local_offset = parse_ClearPortStatus(parentTree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
6663 break;
6664 case PM_ATTR_ID_DATA_PORT_COUNTERS0x0042:
6665 local_offset = parse_DataPortCounters(parentTree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
6666 break;
6667 case PM_ATTR_ID_ERROR_PORT_COUNTERS0x0043:
6668 local_offset = parse_ErrorPortCounters(parentTree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
6669 break;
6670 case PM_ATTR_ID_ERROR_INFO0x0044:
6671 local_offset = parse_ErrorPortInfo(parentTree, tvb, &local_offset, MAD);
6672 break;
6673 default:
6674 return FALSE(0);
6675 }
6676
6677 *offset = local_offset;
6678 return TRUE(!(0));
6679}
6680
6681/* Parse the Method from the MAD Common Header. */
6682static void label_PM_Method(proto_item *PMItem, MAD_t *MAD, packet_info *pinfo)
6683{
6684 const guchar *label = val_to_str_const(MAD->Method, PM_Methods, "(Unknown Perf Method!)");
6685 proto_item_append_text(PMItem, " %s", label);
6686 col_append_str(pinfo->cinfo, COL_INFO, label);
6687}
6688
6689/* Parse the Attribute from the MAD Common Header */
6690static void label_PM_Attribute(proto_item *PMItem, MAD_t *MAD, packet_info *pinfo)
6691{
6692 const guchar *label = val_to_str_const(MAD->AttributeID, PM_Attributes, "Attribute (Unknown Perf Attribute!)");
6693 proto_item_append_text(PMItem, "%s", &label[11]);
6694 col_append_str(pinfo->cinfo, COL_INFO, &label[11]);
6695}
6696/* Parse Performance Management */
6697static void parse_PERF(proto_tree *parentTree, packet_info *pinfo, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset)
6698{
6699 MAD_t MAD;
6700 proto_item *PM_header_item;
6701 proto_tree *PM_header_tree;
6702
6703 if (!parse_MAD_Common(parentTree, pinfo, tvb, offset, &MAD)) {
6704 return;
6705 }
6706
6707 PM_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_pm, tvb, *offset, -1, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6708 PM_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(PM_header_item, ett_pm);
6709
6710 label_PM_Method(PM_header_item, &MAD, pinfo);
6711 label_PM_Attribute(PM_header_item, &MAD, pinfo);
6712
6713 if (!pref_parse_on_mad_status_error && MAD.Status) {
6714 *offset += tvb_captured_length_remaining(tvb, *offset);
6715 return;
6716 }
6717 if (!parse_PM_Attribute(PM_header_tree, tvb, offset, &MAD)) {
6718 expert_add_info_format(pinfo, NULL((void*)0), &ei_opa_mad_no_attribute_dissector,
6719 "Attribute Dissector Not Implemented (0x%x)", MAD.AttributeID);
6720 *offset += tvb_captured_length_remaining(tvb, *offset);
6721 return;
6722 }
6723}
6724
6725/* Parse Image MAD from the Performance Admin class. */
6726static gint parse_Image(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset)
6727{
6728 proto_tree *Image_header_tree = parentTree;
6729
6730 gint local_offset = *offset;
6731
6732 if (!parentTree)
6733 return *offset;
6734
6735 /* ImageID */
6736 proto_tree_add_item(Image_header_tree, hf_opa_ImageID_imageNumber, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6737 local_offset += 8;
6738 proto_tree_add_item(Image_header_tree, hf_opa_ImageID_imageOffset, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6739 local_offset += 4;
6740 proto_tree_add_item(Image_header_tree, hf_opa_reserved32, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
6741 local_offset += 4;
6742 /* End ImageID */
6743
6744 return local_offset;
6745}
6746/* Parse GetGroupList MAD from the Performance Admin class.*/
6747static gint parse_GetGroupList(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD, RMPP_t *RMPP, PA_HEADER_t *PA_HEADER)
6748{
6749 proto_item *GetGroupList_GroupName_item;
6750 proto_tree *GetGroupList_header_tree;
6751 proto_item *GetGroupList_header_item;
6752 gint local_offset = *offset;
6753 guint i;
6754
6755 guint length = ((RMPP->resptime_flags & RMPP_FLAG_LAST_MASK0x04) ? (RMPP->PayloadLength - 20) % STL_MAX_SA_PA_PAYLOAD1992 : STL_MAX_SA_PA_PAYLOAD1992);
6756 guint records = (PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset ? length / (PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset * 8) : 0);
6757
6758 if (!parentTree || RMPP->Type != RMPP_DATA1 ||
6759 (MAD->Method != METHOD_GET_RESP0x81 && MAD->Method != METHOD_GETTABLE_RESP0x92)) {
6760 return *offset;
6761 }
6762 GetGroupList_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_GetGroupList, tvb, local_offset, length, ENC_NA0x00000000);
6763 GetGroupList_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(GetGroupList_header_item, ett_getgrouplist);
6764 proto_tree_add_none_format(GetGroupList_header_tree, hf_opa_GetGroupList, tvb, local_offset, length, "Number of Groups: %u", records);
6765
6766 for (i = 0; i < records; i++) {
6767 GetGroupList_GroupName_item = proto_tree_add_item(GetGroupList_header_tree, hf_opa_GetGroupList_groupName, tvb, local_offset, 64, ENC_ASCII0x00000000 | ENC_NA0x00000000);
6768 local_offset += 64;
6769 proto_item_prepend_text(GetGroupList_GroupName_item, "%3u: ", i + 1);
6770 }
6771 return local_offset;
6772}

7061/* Parse GetGroupConfig MAD from the Performance Admin class.*/
7062static gint parse_GetGroupConfig(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD, RMPP_t *RMPP, PA_HEADER_t *PA_HEADER)
7063{
7064 proto_item *GetGroupConfig_header_item;
7065 proto_tree *GetGroupConfig_header_tree = parentTree;
7066
7067 proto_item *GetGroupConfig_Port_item;
7068 proto_tree *GetGroupConfig_Port_tree;
7069
7070 gint local_offset = *offset;
7071 guint i;
7072
7073 guint length = ((RMPP->resptime_flags & RMPP_FLAG_LAST_MASK0x04) ? (RMPP->PayloadLength - 20) % STL_MAX_SA_PA_PAYLOAD1992 : STL_MAX_SA_PA_PAYLOAD1992);
7074 guint records = (PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset ? length / (PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset * 8) : 0);
7075
7076 if (!parentTree)
7077 return *offset;
7078
7079 if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01 || MAD->Method == METHOD_GETTABLE0x12) {
7080 GetGroupConfig_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_GetGroupConfig, tvb, local_offset, 64 + 16, ENC_NA0x00000000);
7081 proto_item_set_text(GetGroupConfig_header_item, "GroupConfig for %s", tvb_get_string_enc(wmem_file_scope(), tvb, local_offset, 64, ENC_ASCII0x00000000));
7082 GetGroupConfig_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(GetGroupConfig_header_item, ett_getgroupconfig);
7083
7084 proto_tree_add_item(GetGroupConfig_header_tree, hf_opa_GetGroupConfig_groupName, tvb, local_offset, 64, ENC_ASCII0x00000000 | ENC_NA0x00000000);
7085 local_offset += 64;
7086 local_offset = parse_Image(GetGroupConfig_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
7087 } else if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET_RESP0x81 || MAD->Method == METHOD_GETTABLE_RESP0x92) {
7088 GetGroupConfig_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_GetGroupConfig, tvb, local_offset, records * PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset * 8, ENC_NA0x00000000);
7089 GetGroupConfig_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(GetGroupConfig_header_item, ett_getgroupconfig);
7090 for (i = 0; i < records; i++) {
7091 GetGroupConfig_Port_tree = proto_tree_add_subtree_format(GetGroupConfig_header_tree, tvb, local_offset,
7092 PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset * 8, ett_getgroupconfigport, &GetGroupConfig_Port_item, "%3u: ", i);
7093 local_offset = parse_Image(GetGroupConfig_Port_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
7094 proto_tree_add_item(GetGroupConfig_Port_tree, hf_opa_GetGroupConfig_Port_NodeGUID, tvb, local_offset, 8, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
7095 local_offset += 8;
7096 proto_tree_add_item(GetGroupConfig_Port_tree, hf_opa_GetGroupConfig_Port_nodeDesc, tvb, local_offset, 64, ENC_ASCII0x00000000 | ENC_NA0x00000000);
7097 local_offset += 64;
7098 proto_item_append_text(GetGroupConfig_Port_item, "LID: 0x%04x, Port: %u", tvb_get_ntohl(tvb, local_offset), tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset + 4));
7099 proto_tree_add_item(GetGroupConfig_Port_tree, hf_opa_GetGroupConfig_Port_NodeLID, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
7100 local_offset += 4;
7101 proto_tree_add_item(GetGroupConfig_Port_tree, hf_opa_GetGroupConfig_Port_PortNumber, tvb, local_offset, 1, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
7102 local_offset += 1;
7103 proto_tree_add_item(GetGroupConfig_Port_tree, hf_opa_reserved24, tvb, local_offset, 3, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
7104 local_offset += 3;
7105 }
7106 }
7107
7108 return local_offset;
7109}

7111/* Parse GetPortCounters MAD from the Performance Admin class.*/
7112static gint parse_GetPortCounters(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD)
7113{
7114 proto_tree *GetPortCounters_header_tree;
7115 proto_item *GetPortCounters_header_item;

7393/* Parse GetFocusPorts MAD from the Performance Admin class. */
7394static gint parse_GetFocusPorts(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD, RMPP_t *RMPP, PA_HEADER_t *PA_HEADER)
7395{
7396 proto_tree *GetFocusPorts_header_tree;
7397 proto_item *GetFocusPorts_header_item;
7398
7399 proto_tree *GetFocusPorts_Port_tree;
7400 proto_item *GetFocusPorts_Port_item;
7401
7402 gint local_offset = *offset;
7403 guint i = 0;
7404
7405 guint length = ((RMPP->resptime_flags & RMPP_FLAG_LAST_MASK0x04) ? (RMPP->PayloadLength - 20) % STL_MAX_SA_PA_PAYLOAD1992 : STL_MAX_SA_PA_PAYLOAD1992);
7406 guint records = (PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset ? length / (PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset * 8) : 0);
7407
7408 if (!parentTree)
7409 return *offset;
7410
7411 if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET0x01 || MAD->Method == METHOD_GETTABLE0x12) {
7412 GetFocusPorts_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_GetFocusPorts, tvb, local_offset, 64 + 28, ENC_NA0x00000000);
7413 proto_item_set_text(GetFocusPorts_header_item, "Focus Ports for %s", tvb_get_string_enc(wmem_file_scope(), tvb, local_offset, 64, ENC_ASCII0x00000000));
7414 GetFocusPorts_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(GetFocusPorts_header_item, ett_getfocusports);
7415
7416 proto_tree_add_item(GetFocusPorts_header_tree, hf_opa_GetFocusPorts_groupName, tvb, local_offset, 64, ENC_ASCII0x00000000 | ENC_NA0x00000000);
7417 local_offset += 64;
7418 local_offset = parse_Image(GetFocusPorts_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
7419 proto_tree_add_item(GetFocusPorts_header_tree, hf_opa_GetFocusPorts_select, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
7420 local_offset += 4;
7421 proto_tree_add_item(GetFocusPorts_header_tree, hf_opa_GetFocusPorts_start, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
7422 local_offset += 4;
7423 proto_tree_add_item(GetFocusPorts_header_tree, hf_opa_GetFocusPorts_range, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
7424 local_offset += 4;
7425
7426 } else if (MAD->Method == METHOD_GET_RESP0x81 || MAD->Method == METHOD_GETTABLE_RESP0x92) {
7427 GetFocusPorts_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_GetFocusPorts, tvb, local_offset, records * PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset * 8, ENC_NA0x00000000);
7428 GetFocusPorts_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(GetFocusPorts_header_item, ett_getfocusports);
7429 for (i = 0; i < records; i++) {
7430 GetFocusPorts_Port_tree = proto_tree_add_subtree_format(GetFocusPorts_header_tree, tvb, local_offset,
7431 PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset * 8, ett_getfocusportsport, &GetFocusPorts_Port_item, "%3u: ", i);
7432 local_offset = parse_Image(GetFocusPorts_Port_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
7433
7434 proto_item_append_text(GetFocusPorts_Port_item, "LID: %04x, Port %u",
7435 tvb_get_ntohl(tvb, local_offset), tvb_get_guint8(tvb, local_offset + 4));
7436 proto_tree_add_item(GetFocusPorts_Port_tree, hf_opa_GetFocusPorts_nodeLID, tvb, local_offset, 4, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);
7437 local_offset += 4;

7439 local_offset += 1;

7471/* Parse GetImageInfo MAD from the Performance Admin class. */
7472static gint parse_GetImageInfo(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset)
7473{

7475 proto_item *GetImageInfo_header_item;

7477 guint32 numSMs;

7479
7480 gint local_offset = *offset;
7481
7482 if (!parentTree)
7483 return *offset;
7484

7487
7488 local_offset = parse_Image(GetImageInfo_header_tree, tvb, &local_offset);
7489
7490 ts.secs = (time_t)tvb_get_guint64(tvb, local_offset, ENC_BIG_ENDIAN0x00000000);

7562/* Parse GetVFList MAD from the Performance Admin class. */
7563static gint parse_GetVFList(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD, RMPP_t *RMPP, PA_HEADER_t *PA_HEADER)
7564{
7565 proto_item *GetVFList_GroupName_item;
7566 proto_tree *GetVFList_header_tree;
7567 proto_item *GetVFList_header_item;
7568
7569 gint local_offset = *offset;
7570 guint i;
7571
7572 guint length = ((RMPP->resptime_flags & RMPP_FLAG_LAST_MASK0x04) ? (RMPP->PayloadLength - 20) % STL_MAX_SA_PA_PAYLOAD1992 : STL_MAX_SA_PA_PAYLOAD1992);
7573 guint records = (PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset ? length / (PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset * 8) : 0);
7574
7575 if (!parentTree || RMPP->Type != RMPP_DATA1 ||
7576 (MAD->Method != METHOD_GET_RESP0x81 && MAD->Method != METHOD_GETTABLE_RESP0x92)) {
7577 return *offset;
7578 }
7579
7580 GetVFList_header_item = proto_tree_add_item(parentTree, hf_opa_GetVFList, tvb, local_offset, length, ENC_NA0x00000000);
7581 GetVFList_header_tree = proto_item_add_subtree(GetVFList_header_item, ett_getvflist);
7582 proto_tree_add_none_format(GetVFList_header_tree, hf_opa_GetVFList, tvb, local_offset, length, "Number of VFs: %u", records);
7583
7584 for (i = 0; i < records; i++) {
7585 GetVFList_GroupName_item = proto_tree_add_item(GetVFList_header_tree, hf_opa_GetVFList_vfName, tvb, local_offset, 64, ENC_ASCII0x00000000 | ENC_NA0x00000000);
7586 local_offset += 64;
7587 proto_item_prepend_text(GetVFList_GroupName_item, "%3u: ", i + 1);
7588 }
7589
7590 return local_offset;
7591}

7593/* Parse GetVFInfo MAD from the Performance Admin class. */
7594static gint parse_GetVFInfo(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD, RMPP_t *RMPP, PA_HEADER_t *PA_HEADER)
7595{

7652 local_offset += 64;

7654 local_offset += 8;

7657

7659 local_offset += 4;

7760/* Parse GetVFConfig MAD from the Performance Admin class. */
7761static gint parse_GetVFConfig(proto_tree *parentTree, tvbuff_t *tvb, gint *offset, MAD_t *MAD, RMPP_t *RMPP, PA_HEADER_t *PA_HEADER)
7762{

7772 guint records = (PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset ? length / (PA_HEADER->AttributeOffset * 8) : 0);
7773
